ems%20overly%20complex%20and%20constantly%20changing%2C%20which%20created%20a%20culture%20of%20confusion%20among%20the%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EBoeing%20has%20not%20been%20successful%20at%20retaining%20key%20staff%20members%20who%20oversee%20the%20self-certification%20process%2C%20and%20has%20not%20been%20filling%20open%20roles%20quickly%20enough%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20panel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20orders%20Boeing%20to%20come%20up%20with%20an%20action%20plan%20within%20the%20next%20six%20months%20to%20%26quot%3Bcomprehensively%20address%20each%20recommendation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FAA%20made%2053%20total%20recommendations%20for%20how%20the%20company%20should%20not%20just%20improve%20its%20lackluster%20safety%20practices%2C%20but%20bring%20them%20up%20to%20the%20legal%20requirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20sent%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20Boeing%20said%20that%20it%20has%20implemented%20a%20number%20of%20%26quot%3Bfundamental%20changes%26quot%3B%20since%202019%20%26quot%3Bto%20strengthen%20product%20safety%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20added%20that%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20more%20work%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20carefully%20review%20the%20panel's%20assessment%20and%20learn%20from%20their%20findings%2C%20as%20we%20continue%20our%20comprehensive%20efforts%20to%20improve%20our%20safety%20and%20quality%20programs%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffaa-investigated-boeings-safety-culture-and-the-results-arent-great-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708986519000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65dd019f90413ab8e1d6f7a2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffaa-investigated-boeings-safety-culture-and-the-results-arent-great-