ss%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20like%20the%20phone%20rang.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20time%2C%20I%20was%20writing%20to%20Gotham%20Magazine%20and%20Manhattan%20Magazine%2C%20telling%20them%20that%20I%20was%20the%20most%20exclusive%20travel%20company%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20thought%20I%20was%20the%20dumbest%20person%20in%20the%20world%20because%20we%20would%20get%20calls%20from%20people%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20I%20saw%20your%20article.%20I'd%20love%20to%20go%20to%20Disney%2C%26quot%3B%20or%2C%20%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20New%20Jersey%20for%20the%20weekend.%26quot%3B%20And%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20I'm%20sorry%2C%20we're%20so%20busy%2C%20we're%20really%20sold%20out%20this%20season%20with%20high-net-worth%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20had%20no%20clients.%20My%20husband%20would%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BYou're%20an%20idiot.%20Take%20the%20trip.%26quot%3B%20And%20my%20response%20was%2C%20%26quot%3BNo.%20I%20either%20work%20for%20the%20wealthy%20or%20I%20don't.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jaclyn%20and%20her%20husband.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d8bab66080194819f9b63e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22855%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJaclyn%20Sienna%20India%20and%20her%20husband.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Sienna%20Charles%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20me%20three%20years%20to%20get%20a%20client.%20After%20booking%20my%20first%20billionaire%20client%2C%20I%20put%20the%20%2430%2C000%20profit%20toward%20my%20personal%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20people%20would%20think%20I%20was%20an%20idiot%20at%20that%20time%20because%20I%20didn't%20have%20the%20money.%20In%20retrospect%2C%20it%20was%20about%20understanding%20the%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20it%20just%20as%20seriously%20from%20the%20beginning%20as%20I%20do%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20dream%20was%20to%20create%2C%20for%20lack%2