ng%20preference%20call%20where%20we%20get%20to%20know%20them%20and%20build%20out%20their%20profile.%20We%20ask%20questions%20like%3A%20What%20are%20you%20comfortable%20spending%20nightly%20at%20a%20hotel%3F%20Do%20you%20prefer%20contemporary%20hotels%20or%20a%20more%20classical%20style%3F%20What%20are%20your%20favorite%20dining%20times%3F%20Are%20you%20OK%20with%20tasting%20menus%3F%20What%20type%20of%20guide%20do%20you%20like%3F%20We%20collect%20all%20that%2C%20and%20then%20as%20the%20travel%20and%20lifestyle%20requests%20come%20in%2C%20we%20use%20those%20preferences%20to%20help%20clients%20with%20anything%20and%20everything%20throughout%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20learning%20about%20them%20constantly%20and%20using%20information%20to%20improve%20every%20experience.%20Some%20people%20want%20calendar%20invites%2C%20others%20want%20the%20mobile%20app%2C%20and%20others%20only%20want%20to%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20very%20difficult%2C%20complex%20business%20because%20it's%20not%20one%20size%20fits%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20COVID%2C%20we%20helped%20people%20gain%20second%20passports%20and%20pick%20new%20locations%20to%20build%20a%20home.%20We're%20first%20and%20foremost%20a%20travel%20company%2C%20but%20because%20we%20have%20such%20a%20great%20methodology%20of%20sourcing%20like-minded%20vendors%20that%20share%20our%20ethos%2C%20we're%20often%20asked%20to%20help%20clients%20with%20different%20aspects%20of%20their%20lifestyles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22George%20W.%20Bush%20and%20Jaclyn%20Sienna%20Charles%20in%20Ethiopia.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d8ba8dce7f1785b2e36f08%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22851%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGeorge%20W.%20Bush%20and%20Jaclyn%20Sienna%20India%20in%20Ethiopia.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Sienna%20Charles%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20people%20we%20handle%20are%20A-list%20celebrities