B16AHG%20delivers%20a%20great%20balance%20between%20value%20and%20performance%20for%20the%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20has%20a%20speedy%20three-millisecond%20response%20time%20and%20a%20fast%20144Hz%20refresh%20rate%2C%20both%20above%20entry-level%20standards.%20Along%20with%20FreeSync%20technology%2C%20these%20specifications%20ensure%20that%20this%20ZenScreen%20can%20deliver%20a%20quick%20and%20smooth%20experience%20that's%20even%20suitable%20for%20gamers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20that%2C%20the%20monitor%20comes%20with%20decent%20audio%20options%2C%20thanks%20to%20built-in%20speakers%20and%20an%20audio%20jack%20for%20listening%20on%20headphones.%20And%20for%20video%2C%20it%20can%20connect%20to%20devices%20via%20USB-C%20or%20Mini%20HDMI.%20The%20USB%20connection%20is%20also%20how%20the%20display%20receives%20power%2C%20either%20through%20a%20connected%20laptop%20or%20to%20a%20wall%20outlet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20MB16AHG%20has%20also%20been%20built%20with%20ergonomics%20in%20mind.%20A%20handy%20fold-out%20stand%20allows%20for%20tilting%20at%20multiple%20angles%2C%20and%20a%20threaded%20socket%20in%20the%20back%20allows%20it%20to%20be%20mounted%20to%20any%20standard%20tripod.%20The%20screen%20automatically%20orients%20to%20portrait%20or%20landscape%2C%20which%20is%20a%20given%20for%20phones%20nowadays%20but%20not%20always%20for%20portable%20monitors.%20And%20it's%20T%C3%9CV%20Rheinland-certified%20(the%20industry%20standard)%20to%20reduce%20eye%20strain%20through%20flicker-free%20and%20low%20blue%20light%20settings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it's%20not%20quite%20as%20affordable%20as%20our%20budget%20pick%20just%20below%2C%20the%20ZenScreen%20MB16AHG%20is%20the%20best%20portable%20monitor%20for%20anyone%20who%20wants%20a%20great%20all-around%20display%20that%20performs%20well%20for%20a%20broad%20range%20of%20uses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20budget%5C%22%3EBest%20budget%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EViewSonic's%20VA1655%20undercuts%20every%20other%20portable%20monitor%20on%20this%20list.%20Though%20it%20doesn't%20do%20anything%20%3Cem%3Ebetter%3C%2Fem%3E%20than%20our%20other%20picks%2C%20it%20delivers%20impressive%20specs%20for%20its%20low%20price%2C%20making%20it%20a%20worthy%20alternative%20for%20shoppers%20who%20want%20to%20spend%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20strong%20point%20in%20its%20favor%20is%20that%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20lightest%20options%20we%20recommend%2C%20at%20just%201.5%20pounds.%20And%20like%20our%20top%20pick%2C%20the%20VA1655%20features%20a%2015.6-inch%20screen%20with%201080p%20resolution.%20On%20the%20downside%2C%20its%20seven-millisecond%20response%20time%20is%20slightly%20slower%20than%20pricier%20models%2C%20but%20the%20average%20student%20or%20remote%20worker%20probably%20won't%20notice%20any%20screen%20lag.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20monitor's%20peak%20brightness%20is%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20bunch%2C%20just%20on%20the%20OK%20side%20of%20what's%20acceptable%2C%20which%20means%20it's%20fine%20for%20use%20indoors%20but%20won't%20be%20a%20good%20match%20for%20bright%20sunlight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20got%20a%20lower%20native%20bit%20depth%20than%20our%20other%20picks%2C%20which%20means%20it%20can't%20display%20as%20many%20distinct%20colors.%20It%20still%20offers%20decent%20performance%20for%20casual%20multimedia%20use%2C%20but%20we%20don't%20recommend%20this%20unit%20for%20dedicated%20gamers%2C%20photo%20editors%2C%20or%20serious%20movie%20watchers.%20It's%20more%20of%20a%20dependable%20productivity%20workhorse%20for%20tasks%20such%20as%20word%20processing%2C%20coding%2C%20busting%20out%20spreadsheets%2C%20and%20showing%20off%20presentations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20interesting%20feature%20is%20that%20this%20monitor%20is%20capable%20of%20two-way%20charging%2C%20so%20via%20USB-C%2C%20it%20can%20either%20be%20powered%20by%20or%20send%20power%20to%20a%20laptop.%20(For%20the%20latter%20to%20occur%2C%20the%20VA1655%20has%20to%20be%20plugged%20into%20an%20outlet%20or%20appropriately%20strong%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-portable-chargers-power-banks%5C%22%3Epower%20bank%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20monitor%20comes%20with%20a%20case%2C%20plus%20USB-C%20and%20Mini%20HDMI%20cables.%20And%20it%20facilitates%20audio%20listening%20with%20a%203.5mm%20jack%20and%20small%20built-in%20speakers.%20So%20it's%20not%20just%20inexpensive%20but%20respectably%20well-featured.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20gaming%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20gaming%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20Asus's%20ROG%20(Republic%20of%20Gamers)%20brand%20has%20become%20practically%20synonymous%20with%20some%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-gaming-laptop%5C%22%3Ebest%20gaming%20laptops%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-gaming-monitor%5C%22%3Ebest%20gaming%20monitors%3C%2Fa%3E%20you%20can%20buy.%20So%2C%20it%20shouldn't%20be%20a%20huge%20surprise%20that%20the%20company's%2017.3-inch%20ROG%20Strix%20XG17AHP%20earns%20a%20spot%20on%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20best%20portable%20monitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20beast%20sports%20some%20pretty%20sick%20specs%2C%20mostly%20in%20terms%20of%20its%20speed.%20In%20fact%2C%20with%20a%20three-millisecond%20response%20time%20and%20up%20to%20240Hz%20refresh%20rate%2C%20Asus%20claims%20this%20is%20the%20world's%20fastest%20portable%20gaming%20monitor.%20Plus%2C%20with%20adaptive%20sync%20on%20board%2C%20it%20aims%20to%20run%20quickly%20%3Cem%3Eand%3C%2Fem%3E%20tear-free%2C%20so%20you%20get%20a%20smooth%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20distinguishing%20feature%20that%20sets%20this%20portable%20monitor%20apart%20from%20our%20other%20recommendations%20is%20that%20it's%20one%20of%20our%20only%20picks%20blessed%20with%20built-in%20power.%20More%20specifically%2C%20a%20quick-charging%207800mAh%20battery%20that%20Asus%20says%20can%20offer%20around%20three%20hours%20of%20gameplay.%20Thus%2C%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20drain%20power%20from%20a%20connected%20laptop%2C%20which%20is%20a%20nice%20perk%20since%20gaming%20laptops%20are%20infamous%20for%20their%20short%20battery%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOutside%20its%20speed%20and%20battery%2C%20the%20monitor's%20resolution%2C%20color%20gamut%2C%20and%20brightness%20are%20solid%20but%20not%20quite%20top-tier.%20If%20we%20had%20our%20druthers%2C%20the%20display%20would%20be%204K%20rather%20than%201080p%2C%20cover%20the%20larger%20DCI-P3%20color%20gamut%20instead%20of%20just%20sRGB%2C%20and%20offer%20another%20100%20to%20150%20nits%20of%20brightness.%20But%20it's%20still%20nice%20that%20it's%20T%C3%9CV%20certified%20for%20a%20flicker-free%2C%20low-blue%20light%20experience%20to%20help%20reduce%20eye%20strain%20during%20long%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsus%20sells%20two%20versions%20of%20this%20monitor%3A%20the%20Strix%20XG17AHP%20and%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipgf_060319_best-portable-monitors-20%26h%3Dcb1aa2d12063a82b1191b8129717a9cb1a156bdd481fac3505c621cfab364408%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f42525%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fbest-portable-monitor%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Frog.asus.com%252Fus%252Fmonitors%252Fbelow-23-inches%252Frog-strix-xg17ahpe-model%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAHPE%3C%2Fa%3E%20version.%20Both%20are%20virtually%20identical%2C%20with%20the%20only%20difference%20(other%20than%20price)%20being%20that%20the%20former%20includes%20a%20foldable%20tripod%20stand%2C%20and%20the%20latter%20doesn't.%20Although%20we've%20seen%20a%20few%20reports%20complaining%20about%20how%20wobbly%20the%20monitor%20can%20be%20on%20its%20tripod%2C%20it's%20still%20a%20nice%20bonus.%20You%20also%20get%20a%20cover%20(that%20can%20act%20as%20an%20impromptu%20stand%20in%20portrait%20or%20landscape)%20and%20a%20handy%20carry%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20touchscreen%5C%22%3EBest%20touchscreen%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20might%20not%20already%20know%20Espresso%2C%20the%20Australian%20display%20maker%2C%20but%20its%2017%20Pro%20touchscreen%20portable%20monitor%20is%20a%20creative%20professional's%20dream%20that%20can%20rival%20many%20dedicated%20drawing%20tablets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20starters%2C%20it%20features%20a%20gorgeous%2017-inch%204K%20screen.%20The%20durable%20aluminum%20chassis%20and%20scratch-resistant%20glass%20mean%20it%20can%20go%20nearly%20anywhere.%20And%20for%20when%20working%20at%20a%20desk%20or%20table%2C%20it%20includes%20a%20nice%2C%20sturdy%20stand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it%20may%20not%20have%20the%20fastest%20refresh%20rate%20or%20response%20time%2C%20both%20specs%20are%20adequate%20for%20tasks%20outside%20of%20high%20frame-rate%20gaming.%20More%20importantly%2C%20the%2017%20Pro%20conveys%20gorgeous%20images%20and%20video%2C%20thanks%20to%20a%2010-bit%20color%20panel%20and%20support%20for%20the%20wide%20DCI-P3%20gamut.%20Moreover%2C%20its%20450%20nits%20of%20peak%20brightness%20ensures%20those%20colors%20pop%20in%20various%20lighting%20conditions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20capacitive%20touchscreen%2C%20its%20raison%20d'etre%2C%20uses%20what%20Espresso%20calls%20its%20proprietary%20LiveTouch%20technology.%20The%20upshot%20is%20that%20the%2017%20Pro%20excels%20at%20taking%20inputs%20from%20writing%20and%20drawing%2C%20plus%20responding%20to%20various%20gesture%20controls.%20The%20optional%20pen%20accessory%20features%20a%20tail%20eraser%20and%20replaceable%20tip%20and%20is%20sensitive%20to%20tilting%20and%20over%204%2C000%20pressure%20levels.%20It's%20a%20shame%20the%20pen%20doesn't%20come%20included%2C%20but%20you%20can%20purchase%20it%20separately%20for%20%2489%20or%20as%20part%20of%20a%20%241%2C050%20bundle%20that%20also%20includes%20a%20stand%2C%20case%2C%20battery%2C%20and%20paper-like%20screen%20coating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20monitor%20features%20many%20wired%20connectivity%20options%2C%20including%20USB-C%2C%20HDMI%2C%20Mini%20DisplayPort%2C%20and%20DVI-D.%20And%20its%20built-in%20speakers%20automatically%20activate%20when%20the%2017%20Pro%20is%20connected%20to%20a%20secondary%20power%20source%20(i.e.%2C%20your%20laptop%20or%20a%20wall%20outlet).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20Espresso%20includes%20its%20Jot%20software%2C%20which%20works%20in%20tandem%20with%20popular%20productivity%20apps%20(Slides%2C%20PowerPoint%2C%20Keynote%2C%20Evernote%2C%20etc.)%20to%20help%20you%20take%20notes%2C%20draw%2C%20sketch%2C%20mark%20up%2C%20screenshot%2C%20and%20otherwise%20create%20and%20edit%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20wireless%5C%22%3EBest%20wireless%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20a%20portable%20monitor%20that%20can%20work%20completely%20free%20from%20cables%2C%20then%20this%20Ricoh%20model%20is%20just%20what%20you're%20looking%20for.%20It%20supports%20USB-C%20and%20WiFi%205%20(802.11ac)%2C%20so%20it%20can%20connect%20wired%20or%20wirelessly%20to%20Windows%2C%20Mac%2C%20Android%2C%20and%20iOS%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20150BW%20supports%20wireless%20multicasting%20in%20either%20direction.%20This%20means%20the%20display%20can%20handle%20signals%20from%20up%20to%20two%20devices%20simultaneously%2C%20thanks%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fhow-to-cast-windows-desktop-to-tv%5C%22%3EMiracast%3C%2Fa%3E%20functionality.%20And%20it%20supports%20wirelessly%20multicasting%20to%20up%20to%20five%20other%20150BW%20monitors%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20making%20it%20a%20handy%20option%20for%20group%20presentations%20if%20your%20coworkers%20use%20the%20same%20display.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ricoh150BW%20is%20also%20the%20only%20OLED%20monitor%20in%20this%20guide.%20OLED%20panels%20provide%20big%20contrast%20and%20viewing%20angle%20benefits%20over%20LCD%20technology%2C%20and%20OLED%20screens%20are%20used%20on%20many%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-tv%5C%22%3Ebest%20TVs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20scratch-%20and%20shatter-proof%20glass%20display%20features%20multipoint%20capacitive%20touch%20as%20well.%20It's%20pretty%20svelte%20%E2%80%94%20claiming%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20lightest%2015.6-inch%20touchscreen%20portable%20monitors%20on%20the%20market%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20impressive%2C%20considering%20it%20also%20has%20an%20integrated%20battery%20to%20go%20wireless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20the%20listed%20three%20hours%20of%20battery%20life%20isn't%20as%20long%20as%20we'd%20like%20for%20a%20wireless%20monitor.%20That's%20still%20enough%20to%20watch%20a%20movie%2C%20give%20in-person%20presentations%2C%20and%20tackle%20short%20productivity%20sessions%2C%20but%20isn't%20enough%20to%20get%20away%20with%20a%20full%20day%20of%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20monitor's%20fantastic%20color%20gamut%2C%20built-in%201.5-watt%20speakers%2C%20and%20scorching%20max%20response%20time%20of%20one%20millisecond%20make%20it%20a%20solid%20choice%20for%20casual%20gaming.%20That%20said%2C%20the%20refresh%20rate%20is%20limited%20to%2060Hz%2C%20which%20is%20low%20compared%20to%20the%20144Hz-plus%20refresh%20rate%20that%20true%20gaming%20displays%20offer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERicoh%20also%20sells%20a%20compatible%20stylus%20pen%20capable%20of%204%2C096%20levels%20of%20pressure%20sensitivity.%20Given%20the%20price%2C%20we%20wish%20this%20was%20automatically%20bundled%20with%20the%20monitor%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20a%20great%20option%20to%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20test%20portable%20monitors%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20test%20portable%20monitors%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20ViewSonic%20portable%20monitor%20paired%20with%20a%20wireless%20keyboard%20on%20a%20desk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65dcf7ab6080194819fa4900%