ra%20Barter's%20investigation%20into%20whether%20her%20late%20step-grandfather%20Jim%20Mordecai%20was%20a%20killer.%3Cp%3EHBO%20Max%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMax's%20%26quot%3BThe%20Truth%20About%20Jim%2C%26quot%3B%20directed%20by%20Skye%20Borgman%2C%20follows%20Sierra%20Barter's%20investigation%20into%20her%20step-grandfather.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EJim%20Mordecai%2C%20who%20died%20in%202008%2C%20was%20accused%20of%20harassment%20and%20sexual%20assault%20by%20multiple%20women.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBarter%20also%20investigates%20whether%20Mordecai%20may%20have%20been%20the%20infamous%20Zodiac%20Killer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESierra%20Barter%20always%20knew%20her%20grandmother's%20husband%20was%20a%20bad%20man.%20But%20was%20Jim%20Mordecai%20an%20infamous%20serial%20killer%20too%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20the%20question%20at%20the%20crux%20of%20Max's%20%26quot%3BThe%20Truth%20About%20Jim%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20new%20docuseries%20from%20Skye%20Borgman%2C%20the%20critically%20acclaimed%20filmmaker%20behind%20true%20crime%20hits%20like%20%26quot%3BThe%20Girl%20in%20the%20Picture%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BAbducted%20in%20Plain%20Sight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20four-part%20saga%2C%20which%20premiered%20February%2015%2C%20tracks%20Barter's%20investigation%20into%20Mordecai%2C%20a%20former%20high%20school%20teacher%20in%20the%20San%20Francisco%20Bay%20area%20city%20of%20Half%20Moon%20Bay.%20She%20speaks%20to%20Mordecai's%20family%20members%20and%20other%20alleged%20victims%2C%20building%20a%20disturbing%20picture%20of%20a%20man%20who%20many%20say%20bullied%20and%20terrorized%20them%20with%20violence%2C%20threats%2C%20and%20even%20rape%20until%20his%20death%20from%20cancer%20in%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20series%2C%20Mordecai's%20family%20members%20and%20other%20women%20come%20forward%20to%20say%20they%20were%20viciously%20bullied%20and%20sexually%20or%20physically%20abused%20by%20the%20former%20Northern%20California%20teacher%2C%20who%20they%20also%20accuse%20of%20preying%20on%20teenage%20girls.%20One%20of%20his%20daughters%20recounts%20nightmares%20of%20being%20raped%20by%20him%2C%20and%20his%20former%20stepdaughter%2C%20Christi%20Probst%2C%20says%20she%20was%20sexually%20abused%20by%20him%20for%20years%2C%20starting%20when%20she%20was%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Barter%2C%20who%20was%20young%20when%20Mordecai%20died%2C%20the%20investigation%20was%20deeply%20personal%20on%20many%20levels.%20At%20the%20time%20she%20started%20digging%20into%20Mordecai%2C%20she%20says%20she%20was%20healing%20from%20being%20sexually%20assaulted%20for%20the%20second%20time%20in%20her%20life.%20She%20had%20gone%20back%20to%20school%20to%20study%20film%20during%20the%20pandemic%20and%20started%20writing%20about%20her%20family.%20A%20producer%20who%20came%20to%20her%20class%20asked%20whether%20Barter's%20story%20was%20true%20and%20put%20her%20in%20touch%20with%20Imagine%20Entertainment%2C%20a%20production%20company%20that%20in%20turn%20connected%20her%20with%20Borgman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBorgman%2C%20of%20course%2C%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20deeply%20disturbing%20family%20sagas%2C%20and%20she%20gets%20plenty%20of%20pitches%20for%20new%20material.%20What%20immediately%20captivated%20the%20filmmaker%20when%20she%20heard%20Barter's%20story%20was%20how%20survivor-forward%20it%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20three%20generations%20of%20women%20affected%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Borgman%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20referring%20to%20Barter%2C%20Mordecai's%20daughters%20and%20stepdaughters%20(including%20Barter's%20mother%2C%20Shannon%20Barter)%2C%20and%20Mordecai's%20wives%20(including%20Barter's%20grandmother%2C%20Judy%20Mordecai).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLooking%20at%20what%20generational%20trauma%20can%20do%20to%20people%20is%20incredibly%20interesting%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BLooking%20at%20the%20effects%20of%20one%20man%20on%20a%20family%20was%20very%2C%20very%20compelling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThere%20were%20even%20more%20stories%20about%20Mordecai%20that%20didn't%20make%20it%20into%20the%20docuseries%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20flood%20of%20horrific%20stories%20about%20Mordecai%20from%20those%20closest%20to%20him%2C%20not%20everyone%20in%20Half%20Moon%20Bay%20was%20supportive%20of%20Barter's%20digging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20jarring%20scene%20in%20the%20documentary%2C%20Shannon%20Barter%2C%20who%20was%20a%20student%20of%20Mordecai's%20in%20high%20school%20before%20he%20married%20her%20mother%2C%20recalls%20posting%20about%20her%20negative%20experiences%20with%20Mordecai%20in%20a%20Facebook%20group%20and%20asking%20if%20others%20had%20stories%20to%20share.%20The%20majority%20of%20responses%2C%20according%20to%20Shannon%2C%20were%20from%20former%20students%20defending%20Mordecai%20and%20berating%20her%20for%20making%20the%20accusations%20against%20a%20man%20who%20was%20dead%20and%20couldn't%20defend%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20incredibly%20gifted%20at%20painting%20this%20picture%20of%20himself%20as%20this%20very%20athletic%2C%20mentor-type%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20Barter%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BFor%20all%20the%20terrible%20things%20that%20he%20did%20do%2C%20there%20were%20things%20that%20he%20did%20that%20were%20really%20great%20for%20people%20%E2%80%94%20he%20helped%20people%20get%20into%20college.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20really%20a%20matter%20of%20demasking%20Jim%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BJust%20tearing%20down%20that%20facade%20he%20had%20built%20for%20so%20many%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sierra%20Barter%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Truth%20About%20Jim%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65dcf9076080194819fa4990%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBarter%20in%20a%20still%20from%20%26quot%3BThe%20Truth%20About%20Jim.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EMax%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20pushback%2C%20every%20family%20member%20who%20appears%20in%20the%20docuseries%20is%20unanimous%20in%20their%20contention%20that%20Mordecai%20was%20a%20monster.%20In%20addition%20to%20speaking%20with%20her%20own%20mother%20and%20grandmother%2C%20Barter%20interviews%20Jeanne%20Kirkpatrick%2C%20Mordecai's%20second%20wife%3B%20Christi%20and%20Michael%20Probst%2C%20Mordecai's%20former%20stepchildren%20through%20Kirkpatrick's%20previous%20marriage%3B%20and%20Melissa%20and%20Jaime%20Mordecai%2C%20his%20two%20daughters%20with%20Kirkpatrick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMordecai's%20first%20wife%2C%20Shannon%20Yeager%2C%20and%20their%20two%20children%20don't%20appear%20in%20the%20docuseries%2C%20however.%20But%20it's%20not%20because%20they%20disagreed%20with%20how%20he%20was%20portrayed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYeager%2C%20Barter%20says%2C%20was%20unavailable%20to%20shoot%20when%20they%20were%20filming%20due%20to%20personal%20matters.%20%26quot%3BBut%20we've%20had%20conversations%20with%20her.%20She's%20aware.%20She%20agrees%20he%20was%20not%20a%20great%20guy%2C%20and%20she%20has%20a%20ton%20of%20stories%20of%20her%20own%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYeager%20and%20Mordecai's%20daughter%20died%20years%20ago.%20Their%20son%20was%20also%20unavailable%20for%20filming%20but%20had%20plenty%20of%20negative%20stories%20about%20his%20father%20as%20well%2C%20according%20to%20Barter.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20not%20on%20team%20Jim%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWas%20Jim%20Mordecai%20the%20Zodiac%20Killer%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20still%20from%20%26quot%3BThe%20Truth%20About%20Jim%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65dcf9386080194819fa49a0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBarter's%20investigation%20board.%3Cp%3EMax%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20fleshing%20out%20a%20portrait%20of%20the%20ways%20Mordecai%20harmed%20his%20own%20family%2C%20Barter%20set%20out%20to%20investigate%20the%20long-simmering%20suspicions%20she%20and%20her%20mother%20shared%20that%20Mordecai's%20crimes%20had%20escalated%20to%20murder.%20In%20the%20docuseries%2C%20we%20see%20her%20track%20down%20leads%20and%20speak%20to%20witnesses%20involved%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sfgate.com%2Funsolved%2Farticle%2Fsearch-continues-for-Santa-Rosa-hitchhiker-murders-16991943.php%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESanta%20Rosa%20Hitchhiker%20Murders%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20slew%20of%20killings%20in%20the%201970s%20that%20local%20authorities%20theorized%20were%20all%20committed%20by%20one%20serial%20killer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20shocking%20scene%2C%20Barter%20comes%20face%20to%20face%20with%20a%20woman%20named%20Mary%2C%20whose%20two%20friends%20were%20believed%20to%20be%20victims%20of%20the%20Santa%20Rosa%20killer%20decades%20earlier.%20Mary%20recounts%20seeing%20a%20man%20watching%20her%20friends%20at%20the%20ice%20rink%20shortly%20before%20they%20were%20abducted.%20When%20Barter%20shows%20her%20a%20photo%20of%20Mordecai%2C%20Mary%20reacts%20strongly%20and%20says%20he%20does%20look%20like%20the%20man%20she%20saw%20all%20those%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarter%20is%20visibly%20shaken%20by%20the%20reveal%2C%20and%20the%20moment%20is%20electric.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20one%20of%20the%20hardest%20moments%20for%20sure%20on%20the%20show.%20Just%20a%20moment%20that%20was%20captured%20so%20raw%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20tells%20BI.%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20felt%20really%20derailed%20in%20that%20moment%2C%20I%20was%20almost%20like%2C%20'Okay%2C%20what's%20going%20on%3F%20Who's%20joking%20with%20me%20right%20now%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20an%20experience%20I%20had%20no%20tools%20for%2C%20no%20language%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%20%26quot%3BI've%20never%20been%20around%20anything%20like%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBorgman%2C%20for%20her%20part%2C%20said%20witnessing%20Barter's%20conversation%20with%20Mary%2C%20effectively%20the%20first%20true%20piece%20of%20evidence%20that%20Mordecai%20may%20indeed%20have%20been%20a%20killer%2C%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bbizarre%2C%20surreal%20experience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20little%20bit%20shocking.%20Sierra%20may%20have%20even%20said%20to%20us%2C%20'Did%20you%20set%20this%20up%3F%20Did%20you%20tell%20her%3F'%26quot%3B%20Borgman%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20there%20was%20that%20moment%20of%20disbelief%20that%20there%20%3Cem%3Eis%3C%2Fem%3E%20this%20potential%20connection%20that%20may%20be%20there.%20Like%2C%20'Holy%20cow%2C%20this%20is%20something%20real.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20Barter%20even%20considers%20the%20possibility%20that%20Mordecai%20may%20have%20been%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-citizens-crack-infamous-zodiac-killer-message-2020-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZodiac%20Killer%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20most%20infamous%20unidentified%20murderers%20of%20all%20time.%20Borgman%20and%20Barter%20decided%20to%20follow%20that%20thread%2C%20unraveling%20it%20in%20real%20time%20during%20filming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20something%20that%20Sierra%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20her%20family%20thought%20could%20be%20a%20possibility%2C%26quot%3B%20Borgman%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BWe%20set%20out%20early%20on%20to%20say%2C%20'Let's%20look%20at%20all%20the%20possibilities.%20Let's%20not%20just%20put%20something%20away%20because%20we%20don't%20think%20it%20could%20be%20this.%20Let's%20dive%20into%20it%2C%20let's%20do%20the%20investigation%2C%20let's%20ask%20the%20questions.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSierra%20never%20was%20like%2C%20'I'm%20certain%20it's%20this.'%20She%20was%20just%20like%2C%20'I%20want%20to%20find%20the%20truth%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20the%20Zodiac%20theory%20doesn't%20pan%20out%20%E2%80%94%20Barter%20meets%20with%20Zodiac%20expert%20Mike%20Butterfield%2C%20who%20concludes%20that%20there%20isn't%20compelling%20evidence%20to%20link%20Mordecai%20to%20the%20crimes.%20But%20in%20the%20final%20episode%20of%20the%20docuseries%2C%20Barter%20finally%20compiles%20all%20of%20her%20evidence%20linking%20Mordecai%20to%20the%20Santa%20Rosa%20killings%20and%20turns%20it%20over%20to%20the%20Sonoma%20County%20Sheriff's%20Office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20closing%20tag%20says%20that%20the%20investigation%20is%20ongoing%2C%20and%20Borgman%20and%20Barter%20confirm%20that%20there%20are%20still%20no%20updates%20on%20whether%20or%20not%20Mordecai%20was%20the%20murderer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20though%2C%20proving%20whether%20Mordecai%20was%20a%20killer%20isn't%20the%20main%20point%20of%20the%20docuseries.%20It's%20about%20healing%20%E2%80%94%20Barter's%20own%20journey%20to%20healing%20after%20her%20sexual%20assaults%2C%20and%20how%20she%20facilitates%20her%20fractured%20family's%20healing%20after%20decades%20of%20trauma%20at%20Mordecai's%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20movingly%2C%20we%20see%20Barter's%20mother%20and%20grandmother%20make%20inroads%20after%20years%20of%20estrangement%20due%20to%20Judy's%20decision%20to%20remain%20married%20to%20Mordecai%2C%20who%20Shannon%20says%20harassed%20her%20both%20before%20and%20during%20the%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Judy%20Mordecai%2C%20Sierra%20Barter%2C%20and%20Shannon%20Barter%20in%20a%20still%20from%20%26quot%3BThe%20Truth%20About%20Jim%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ce75c4f533b039a88441cd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221072%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJudy%20Mordecai%2C%20Barter%2C%20and%20Shannon%20Barter.%3Cp%3EMax%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMordecai's%20third%20wife%2C%20Judy%2C%20was%20married%20to%20h