20will%20put%20the%20social%20networking%20platform%20to%20the%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20released%20a%20statement%20on%20Sunday%20outlining%20a%20new%20plan%20to%20ensure%20election%20integrity%20with%20the%20EU%20Parliament%20elections%20taking%20place%20June%206%20through%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20each%20election%20is%20unique%2C%20this%20work%20drew%20on%20key%20lessons%20we%20have%20learned%20from%20more%20than%20200%20elections%20around%20the%20world%20since%202016%2C%26quot%3B%20Marco%20Pancini%2C%20head%20of%20EU%20affairs%20at%20Meta%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabout.fb.com%2Fnews%2F2024%2F02%2Fhow-meta-is-preparing-for-the-eus-2024-parliament-elections%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPancini%20said%20that%20Meta%20is%20focusing%20on%20three%20key%20areas%3A%20misinformation%2C%20influence%20operations%2C%20and%20generative%20AI%20abuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fmisinformation-vs-disinformation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMisinformation%20refers%20to%20the%20spread%20of%20incorrect%20information%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20influence%20operations%20refers%20to%20deceptive%20campaigns.%20The%20company%20has%20so%20far%20partnered%20with%2026%20fact-checking%20organizations%20and%20releases%20a%20quarterly%20report%20on%20threat%20findings%2C%20according%20to%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20recently%2C%20the%20company%20is%20fine-tuning%20its%20approach%20to%20GenAI.%20Meta%20joined%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpartnershiponai.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPartnership%20on%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20platform%20designed%20to%20promote%20guidelines%20and%20best%20practices.%20It%20also%20signed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aielectionsaccord.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETech%20Accord%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20prevent%20deceptive%20AI%20