bles%20to%20fix%20Gemini's%20problems%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20this%20seems%20like%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20an%20endless%20Whac-A-Mole.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20in%20part%20because%20it's%20inherently%20hard%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20an%20AI%20engine%20spits%20out%20(including%20when%20it%20will%20simply%20make%20things%20up%20%E2%80%94%20or%20as%20the%20industry%20describes%20it%2C%20to%20%26quot%3Bhallucinate%26quot%3B).%20And%20Google's%20peers%20at%20Meta%20and%20OpenAI%2FMicrosoft%20have%20had%20similar%20struggles%20trying%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F07%2F27%2Fbusiness%2Fai-chatgpt-safety-research.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erein%20in%20Bad%20Answers%20and%20Behaviors%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20also%20going%20to%20be%20a%20problem%20for%20Google%20because%20it%20has%20already%20said%20it%20%3Cem%3Eis%3C%2Fem%3E%20trying%20to%20influence%20the%20way%20its%20AI%20produces%20results.%20And%20that's%20going%20to%20be%20red%20meat%20for%20anyone%20who%20wants%20to%20argue%20that%20Google%20%E2%80%94%20or%20any%20other%20Big%20Tech%20company%20%E2%80%94%20is%20%26quot%3Btoo%20woke.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20after%20getting%20similar%20criticism%20about%20the%20way%20Gemini%20handled%20race%20when%20it%20came%20to%20AI-generated%20images%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-gemini-ai-pause-image-generation-people-woke-complaints-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20%26quot%3Bpaused%26quot%3B%20Gemini's%20ability%20to%20create%20images%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20the%20company%20acknowledged%20that%20it%20had%20consciously%20trained%20Gemini%20to%20respond%20to%20some%20of%20the%20common%20criticisms%20of%20AI%20engines%20%E2%80%94%20that%20the%20output%20they%20create%20can%20be%20biased%20because%20they're%20trained%20on%20biased%20or%20limited%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20our%20users%20come%20from%20all%20over%20the%20world%2C%20we%20want%20it%20to%20work%20well%20for%20everyone.%20If%20you%20ask%20for%20a%20picture%20of%20football%20players%2C%20or%20someone%20walking%20a%20dog%2C%20you%20may%20want%20to%20receive%20a%20range%20of%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.google%2Fproducts%2Fgemini%2Fgemini-image-generation-issue%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20Prabhakar%20Raghavan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Google%20senior%20vice%20president%20who%20runs%20its%20search%20and%20news%20products%2C%20among%20other%20things.%20%26quot%3BYou%20probably%20don't%20just%20want%20to%20only%20receive%20images%20of%20people%20of%20just%20one%20type%20of%20ethnicity%20(or%20any%20other%20characteristic).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERaghavan%20said%20Google's%20attempts%20to%20correct%20for%20that%20were%20well-meaning%20but%20%26quot%3Bled%20the%20model%20to%20overcompensate%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20and%20be%20over-conservative%20in%20others%2C%20leading%20to%20images%20that%20were%20embarrassing%20and%20wrong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERemember%20that%20after%20several%20days%20of%20terrible%20press%20over%20dumb%20image%20generations%2C%20Google%20eventually%20pulled%20Gemini's%20image%20generation%20feature%20to%20try%20to%20make%20the%20story%20go%20away%20(and%2For%2C%20to%20be%20more%20generous%2C%20to%20fix%20Gemini's%20problems).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPulling%20Gemini%20altogether%20would%20be%20a%20considerable%20black%20eye%20for%20the%20company%2C%20and%20one%20I%20think%20it%20will%20be%20incredibly%20reluctant%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%20it's%20open%20season%20on%20Gemini%2C%20and%20you%20can%20rest%20assured%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20on%20the%20internet%20are%20going%20to%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20trying%20to%20find%20other%20examples%20of%20rogue%20wokeness.%20I'm%20not%20sure%20how%20Google%20patches%20this%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-gemini-woke-images-ai-chatbot-criticism-controversy-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708978823000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65dcef9790413ab8e1d6ee6e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-gemini-woke-images-ai-chatbot-criticism-controversy-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Some%20critics%20say%20Google's%20culture%20is%20overly%20influenced%20by%20left-leaning%20workers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22pkafka%40insider.com%20(Peter%20Kafka)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A60%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-gemini-woke-images-ai-chatbot-criticism-controversy-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Boeing%20review%20finds%20'disconnect'%20on%20safety%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708978209000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F5162%2Fproduction%2F_132743802_gettyimages-1953492138.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-68409029%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20report%20ordered%20by%20the%20government%20finds%20%26quot%3Bgaps%20in%20Boeing's%20safety%20journey%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A69%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-68409029%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-68409029.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-68409029.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20couple%20on%20hijacked%20boat%20feared%20killed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708978083000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F15328%2Fproduction%2F_132742868_missinguscouple.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68407454%22%2C%22summ