%20Delhi's%20Sir%20Ganga%20Ram%20Hospital%20took%20out%2039%20coins%20and%2037%20magnets%20from%20a%20man's%20intestine%20by%20surgery.%20The%20patient%2C%20who%20was%20suffering%20from%20a%20psychiatric%20illness%2C%20reportedly%20swallowed%20the%20coins%20and%20magnets%20under%20the%20assumption%20that%20zinc%20helps%20in%20body-building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20came%20to%20light%20when%20a%2026-year-old%20patient%20came%20to%20the%20emergency%20ward%20of%20Sir%20Ganga%20Ram%20Hospital%20with%20complaints%20of%20repeated%20vomiting%20and%20abdominal%20pain%20for%20more%20than%2020%20days.%20The%20patient%20was%20also%20not%20able%20to%20eat%20anything.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20patient%20was%20first%20attended%20by%20the%20senior%20consultant%2C%20Dr%20Tarun%20Mittal%20in%20the%20outpatient%20department.%20The%20patient's%20relatives%20said%20that%20he%20had%20a%20history%20of%20eating%20coins%20and%20magnets%20for%20the%20past%20few%20weeks.%20The%20patient%20was%20also%20on%20treatment%20for%20a%20known%20case%20of%20psychiatric%20illness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20patient's%20relatives%20had%20an%20x-ray%20of%20his%20abdomen%2C%20which%20showed%20radio-opaque%20shadows%20in%20his%20abdomen%20with%20the%20shape%20of%20coins%20and%20magnets.%20A%20CT%20scan%20of%20the%20abdomen%20showed%20a%20huge%20load%20of%20coins%20and%20magnets%20causing%20blockage%20of%20the%20intestine.%20The%20patient%20was%20immediately%20prepared%20for%20the%20surgery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20surgery%2C%20it%20was%20found%20that%20the%20magnets%20and%20coins%20were%20present%20in%20the%20small%20intestine%20in%20two%20different%20loops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20magnetic%20effect%20pulled%20the%20two%20loops%20together%20and%20eroded%20it.%20The%20intestines%20were%20opened%20and%20the%20coins%20and%20magnets%20were%20taken%20out.%20Both%20the%20loops%20were%20rejoined%20by%20two%20different%20anastomoses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20stomach%20was%20inspected%20and%20a%20huge%20load%20of%20coins%20and%20magnets%20were%20also%20found%20there.%20His%20stomach%20was%20subsequently%20opened%20up%20and%20all%20the%20coins%20were%20extracted%20and%20his%20stomach%20was%20repaired.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoctors%20said%20that%20a%20total%20of%2039%20coins%20(Rs%201%2C%202%2C%205%20coins)%20and%2037%20magnets%20(heart%2C%20spherical%2C%20star%2C%20bullet%20and%20triangle%20shapes)%20were%20recovered%20from%20his%20stomach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors%20took%20an%20operative%20X-ray%20of%20the%20patient%20after%20the%20surgery%2C%20which%20showed%20that%20all%20the%20foreign%20bodies%20had%20been%20removed.%20They%20also%20said%20that%20the%20patient%20tolerated%20the%20procedure%20well%20and%20was%20discharged%20in%20healthy%20condition%20after%20seven%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20probing%20the%20patient%2C%20he%20said%20that%20he%20had%20ingested%20the%20coins%20and%20magnets%20because%20he%20thought%20that%20zinc%20helps%20in%20body-building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20coins%20contained%20zinc%20and%20he%20ingested%20the%20magnets%20so%20that%20the%20coins%20would%20stay%20in%20the%20intestine%20to%20facilitate%20more%20absorption%20of%20zinc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20of%20doctors%20at%20Sir%20Ganga%20Ram%20Hospital%20included%20Dr%20Tarun%20Mittal%2C%20Dr%20Ashish%20Dey%20and%20Dr%20Anmol%20Ahuja%20(consultants)%3B%20Dr%20Vikram%20Singh%20(clinical%20assistant)%3B%20Dr%20Tanushree%20and%20Dr%20Karthik%20(residents).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708976760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-01%2Fdu0tfgj_surgery-generic-afp_625x300_11_January_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fzinc-helps-in-body-building-delhi-man-swallows-39-coins-37-magnets-5133354%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Doc