B%20to%20prevent%20undue%20influences%20--%20a%20frequently%20occurring%20situation%20in%20the%20chequered%20politics%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20measures%20were%20not%20so%20drastic.%20The%20ruling%20Congress%20there%20has%20issued%20a%20whip%20to%20its%20MLAs%20for%20election%20on%20its%20sole%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seat%20--%20a%20move%20that%20has%20drawn%20sneers%20from%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Samajwadi%20Party%20--%20the%20main%20Opposition%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20--%20meanwhile%20says%20all%20is%20well%2C%20even%20though%20sources%20say%20at%20least%2010%20of%20the%20party's%20MLAs%20are%20ready%20to%20cross-vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20BJP%20and%20the%20SP%20have%20the%20numbers%20to%20send%20seven%20and%20three%20members%20unopposed%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20But%20the%20BJP%20upped%20stakes%20by%20fielding%20Sanjay%20Seth%20--%20a%20former%20SP%20member%20and%20industrialist%20--%20as%20its%20eighth%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20elected%2C%20a%20candidate%20from%20the%20state%20needs%20nearly%2037%20first%20preference%20votes.%20Leaders%20of%20the%20BJP%20have%20claimed%20that%20at%20least%2010%20MLAs%20of%20the%20SP%20are%20in%20touch%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SP%20has%20fielded%20actor-MP%20Jaya%20Bachchan%2C%20retired%20IAS%20officer%20Alok%20Ranjan%20and%20Dalit%20leader%20Ramji%20Lal%20Suman.%20The%20decision%20has%20apparently%20alienated%20its%20ally%20Apna%20Dal%20(Kamerawadi)%20leader%20Pallavi%20Patel%2C%20who%20earlier%20said%20she%20would%20not%20vote%20as%20she%20did%20not%20agree%20with%20the%20decision%20to%20field%20Ms%20Bachchan%20and%20Mr%20Ranjan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20numbers%20had%20ensured%20smooth%20sailing%20for%20the%20Congress%20in%20four%20of%20Karnataka's%20three%20seats%2C%20the%20BJP-Janata%20Dal%20Secular%20alliance%20queered%20the%20pitch%20by%20fielding%20a%20second%20candidate.%20In%20case%20there%20were%20four%20candidates%2C%20each%20needed%2045%20votes%20to%20win%2C%20but%20in%20case%20of%20more%20candidates%2C%20preference%20votes%20kick%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20134%20MLAs%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%2066%20and%20the%20JD(S)%2019%2C%20while%20others%20account%20for%20four.%20Of%20the%20four%2C%20the%20Congress%20claims%20the%20support%20of%20two%20Independents%20and%20Darshan%20Puttanaiah%20from%20Sarvodaya%20Karnataka%20Paksha%2C%20and%20is%20confident%20of%20winning%20three%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20the%20Congress%20shifted%20all%20its%20MLAs%20to%20a%20hotel%2C%20marking%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20state's%20trademark%20resort%20politics.%20All%20parties%20have%20issued%20whips%20to%20their%20MLAs%20ahead%20of%20today's%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Himachal%2C%20the%20candidate%20for%20whom%20the%20Congress%20would%20be%20battling%20is%20the%20party's%20senior%20leader%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%2C%20against%20whom%20the%20BJP%20has%20fielded%20its%20core%20committee%20member%20Harsh%20Mahajan.%20While%20the%20Congress%20has%20a%20clear%20majority%20with%2040%20MLAs%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%2025%20members.%20Three%20MLAs%20are%20Independents%20of%20whom%20two%20are%20BJP%20rebels.%20The%20BJP%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20is%20now%20eyeing%20dissatisfied%20Congress%20MLAs%20to%20win%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20election%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20prestige%20battle%20for%20Chief%20Minister%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu%2C%20who%20took%20over%20the%20reins%20of%20the%20state%20after%20last%20year's%20assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E56%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seats%20across%2015%20states%20were%20to%20get%20new%20members%2C%2041%20of%20whom%20have%20already%20been%20elected%20unopposed.%20The%20voting%20for%20the%20rest%20will%20be%20held%20today%20from%209%20am%20to%204%20pm.%20Counting%20will%20begin%20at%205%20pm%20and%20the%20results%20are%20expected%20late%20in%20the%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20BJP%20holds%2028%20of%20the%2056%20seats%20--including%20the%20one%20left%20vacant%20by%20party%20lawmaker%20Kirodi%20Lal%20Meena%2C%20who%20has%20become%20a%20minister%20in%20Rajasthan.%20After%20elections%2C%20it%20will%20have%20at%20least%2029%20seats.%20In%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20INDIA%20bloc%20will%20gain%20two%20seats%20as%20the%20SP%20is%20expected%20to%20improve%20its%20tally%20from%20one%20to%20three%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708973640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fum6j1rso_new-parliament-building_625x300_19_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcross-voting-likely-in-rajya-sabha-polls-congress-sp-on-red-alert-5132524%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three%20seats%20in%20two%20Congress-ruled%20states%20and%20one%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20are%20in%20for%20a%20tough%20fight%20during%20Tuesday's%20Rajya%20Sabha%20polls.%20Sources%20have%20indicated%20that%20cross-voting%20by%20Opposition%20MLAs%20are%20very%20likely.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcross-voting-likely-in-rajya-sabha-polls-congress-sp-on-red-alert-5132524%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcross-voting-likely-in-rajya-sabha-polls-congress-sp-on-red-alert-5132524%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcross-voting-likely-in-rajya-sabha-polls-congress-sp-on-red-alert-5132524%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Woman%20in%20Arabic-script%20dress%20saved%20from%20mob%20in%20Pakistan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708973418000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108022068%2Cimgsize-939913.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fwoman-in-arabic-script-dress-saved-from-mob-in-pakistan%2Farticleshow%2F108022030.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3