ms%20largely%20aiming%20to%20ensure%20stability%20and%20both%20nations%20recognised%20their%20constitutions%20as%20%26quot%3Bliving%20documents%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBangladesh's%20apex%20court%20judges%20took%20part%20in%20the%20conference%2C%20which%20drew%20many%20jurists%2C%20senior%20lawyers%2C%20and%20government%20leaders%20including%20Law%20Minister%20Anisul%20Huq.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20shared%20tradition%20aims%20to%20ensure%20stability%2C%20but%20when%20stability%20is%20desired%2C%20the%20stability%20must%20never%20be%20confused%20with%20stagnation%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20recognise%20our%20constitutions%20are%20living%20documents.%20The%20constitutions%20of%20Bangladesh%20and%20India%20proclaim%20that%20they%20are%20'given%20to%20the%20people%20by%20the%20people%20themselves'%20as%20citizens%20of%20sovereign%20nations%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%2C%20Supreme%20Court%20judges%20Justice%20Aniruddha%20Bose%20and%20Justice%20Dipankar%20Dutta%20were%20also%20present%20during%20the%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20said%20the%20Indian%20and%20Bangladeshi%20court%20systems%20should%20encourage%20the%20enhanced%20practice%20of%20mediation%20for%20dispute%20resolution%2C%20discarding%20%26quot%3Badversarial%20litigations%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20we%20need%20to%20ensure%20that%20we%20look%20into%20the%20needs%20of%20our%20society%2C%20ensure%20social%20growth%20and%20social%20progress%20by%20allowing%20our%20marginalised%20groups%20to%20come%20to%20the%20mainstream%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Chief%20Justice%2C%20explaining%20how%20the%20judge's%20role%20in%20the%20post-colonial%20era%20was%20undergoing%20a%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20address%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20said%20her%20government%20has%20made%20the%20judiciary%20totally%20independent%2C%20separating%20it%20from%20the%20administration%20by%20allocating%20a%20separate%20budget%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708967700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fbo0hsb0o_chief-justice-1200_625x300_26_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffollowing-indian-supreme-court-top-bangladesh-official-to-chief-justice-dy-chandrachud-5132636%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Appreciating%20the%20live%20streaming%20of%20court%20proceedings%2C%20virtual%20hearing%20and%20use%20of%20technology%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%2C%20a%20top%20Bangladesh%20official%20told%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20that%20they%20are%20closely%20following%20the%20Indian%20Supreme%20Court.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffollowing-indian-supreme-court-top-bangladesh-official-to-chief-justice-dy-chandrachud-5132636%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffollowing-indian-supreme-court-top-bangladesh-official-to-chief-justice-dy-chandrachud-5132636%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffollowing-indian-supreme-court-top-bangladesh-official-to-chief-justice-dy-chandrachud-5132636%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tripura%20Govt%20Suspends%20Chief%20Wildlife%20Warden%20Over%20Akbar-Sita%20Row%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17121846%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-16-at-10.43.15-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20BJP-ruled%20Tripura%20state%20government%20on%20February%2024%20suspended%20its%20Chief%20Wildlife%20Warden%20Prabin%20Lal%20Agrawal%20for%20recording%20the%20names%20of%20a%20pair%20of%20lions%20as%20Akbar%20and%20Sita%2C%20as%