0Sita%20in%20the%20dispatch%20register%20before%20sending%20them%20to%20West%20Bengal%2C%20per%20the%20report.%20Agrawal%20is%20Tripura%E2%80%99s%20Chief%20Wildlife%20Warden%2C%20one%20of%20the%20topmost%20designations%20in%20the%20state%20forest%20department.%20He%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftripura.gov.in%2Findian-forest-service-cadre-tripura%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ealso%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20Principal%20Chief%20Conservator%20of%20Forests%20(Wildlife%20and%20Tourism).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20February%2016%2C%20the%20local%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20(VHP)%20chapter%20filed%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbengal-vishwa-hindu-parishad-sita-akbar-lion%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epetition%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20that%20later%20went%20as%20a%20public%20interest%20litigation%20to%20the%20Kolkata%20High%20Court%20%E2%80%93%20regarding%20the%20naming%20of%20the%20pair%20as%20Akbar%20and%20Sita.%20VHP%20district%20chief%20Dulal%20Chandra%20Ray%20had%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20naming%20came%20as%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20Hindu%20religion%3A%20Akbar%20is%20the%20name%20of%20a%20Mughal%20emperor%2C%20and%20Sita%20is%20a%20character%20in%20the%20Hindu%20epic%20Ramayan%2C%20also%20revered%20as%20a%20deity%20in%20the%20religion.%20The%20High%20Court%2C%20while%20hearing%20the%20case%2C%20said%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccontroversy%E2%80%9D%20could%20have%20been%20avoided.%20It%20also%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwhy-name-animals-after-gods-historical-figures-asks-kolkata-hc-suggests-changing-lions-names%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Easked%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20who%20had%20named%20the%20animals%20in%20such%20a%20way%20and%20caused%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccontroversy%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESenior%20forest%20official%20suspended%3C%2Fb%