0of%20Sab-e-Baraat%20prayers.%20Photo%3A%20Mirwaiz%20Manzil%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20watering%20down%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20authorities%20in%20Kashmir%20have%20repeatedly%20prevented%20worshippers%20from%20offering%20congregational%20prayers%20at%20the%20Jama%20Masjid%20purportedly%20due%20to%20apprehensions%20of%20law%20and%20order%20problems%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20downtown%20Srinagar%E2%80%99s%20Nowhatta%20locality%2C%20where%20the%20mosque%20is%20located.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20normal%20times%2C%20the%2014th%20century%20architectural%20marvel%2C%20which%20has%20been%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20contested%20political%20past%2C%20used%20to%20be%20bustling%20with%20both%20male%20and%20female%20worshippers%20on%20Fridays%20and%20other%20important%20days%20of%20the%20Islamic%20calendar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20after%20the%20Article%20370%20move%2C%20the%20mosque%20has%20been%20often%20closed%20by%20authorities%20on%20such%20occasions%20and%20a%20posse%20of%20gun-toting%20security%20personnel%20are%20deployed%20in%20strength%20at%20its%20main%20gates%20to%20turn%20away%20any%20worshippers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20authorities%20have%20justified%20the%20crackdown%20citing%20fears%20of%20%E2%80%9Claw%20and%20order%20problems%E2%80%9D%20in%20and%20around%20the%20mosque%20which%20used%20to%20be%20an%20epicentre%20of%20anti-India%20and%20pro-freedom%20sentiment%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20mosque%E2%80%99s%20managing%20body%20has%20termed%20the%20%E2%80%9Crepeated%20action%E2%80%9D%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Cattack%E2%80%9D%20on%20dissent%20and%20religious%20rights%20of%20Kashmiri%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20High%20Court%20granted%20the%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20administration%20%E2%80%9Clast%20and%20final%20opportunity%E2%80%9D%20to%20respond%20to%20a%20habeas%20corpus%20petition%20which%20challenges%20the%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20confinement%E2%80%9D%20of%20Mirw