se%20arrest.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fsrinagars-jamia-masjid-forcibly-closed-ahead-of-shab-e-baraat-prayers%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2213%20Years%20After%20Hiroshima%2C%20US%20Lost%203%20Nukes%2C%20One%2070%20Times%20Stronger%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20lost%20at%20least%20three%20nuclear%20bombs%20that%20have%20never%20been%20located.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20one%20of%20these%20undetonated%20thermonuclear%2C%20or%20hydrogen%2C%20bombs%20lies%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20Philippine%20Sea.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20it%20is%20believed%20to%20be%2070%20times%20more%20powerful%20than%20the%20one%20dropped%20on%20Hiroshima%20during%20the%20Second%20World%20War.%20These%20three%20bombs%20were%20lost%20within%20a%20period%20of%2010%20years%20-%20from%201958%20to%201968%20-%20but%20were%20never%20found%2C%20the%20outlet%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%201950%2C%20there%20have%20been%20more%20than%20two%20dozen%20%26quot%3BBroken%20Arrow%26quot%3B%20incidents%20involving%20accidental%20launch%2C%20theft%20or%20detonation%20or%20loss%20of%20US%20nuclear%20weapons.%20But%20only%20three%20have%20been%20documented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20bomb%20went%20missing%20in%20February%201958%20near%20the%20Tybee%20Island%2C%20Georgia.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Ffuture%2Farticle%2F20220804-the-lost-nuclear-bombs-that-no-one-can-find%5C%22%3EThe%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20was%20jettisoned%20to%20reduce%20the%20plane's%20weight%20for%20a%20safer%20landing.%20Then%2C%20on%20December%205%2C%201965%2C%20a%20bomber%20plane%2C%20pilot%20and%20nuclear%20weapon%20slipped%20off%20the%20side%20of%20a%20carrier%20boat%20in%20the%20Philippine%20Sea%2C%20never%20to%20be%20seen%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20documented%20%26quot%3BBroken%20Arrow%26quot%3B%20incident%20took%20place%20on%20May%2022%2C%201968%2C%20when%20a%20nuclear%20attack%20submarine%20the%20USS%20Scorpion%20sank%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20Atlantic%2C%20with%20the%20loss%20of%2099%20lives%20-%20and%20two%20nuclear-tipped%20torpedoes.%20The%20submarine%20and%20the%20weapons%20have%20never%20been%20recovered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20extensive%20search%20efforts%20by%20American%20teams%2C%20the%20whereabouts%20of%20the%20missing%20bombs%20remained%20unknown%2C%20fuelling%20fears%20of%20a%20potential%20environmental%20catastrophe%20and%20geopolitical%20fallout.%20Speculation%20ran%20rampant%2C%20with%20theories%20ranging%20from%20espionage%20and%20sabotage%20to%20a%20cover-up%20by%20government%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20risk%20of%20them%20causing%20a%20nuclear%20explosion%20is%20thought%20to%20be%20low%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20of%20the%20three%20missing%20American%20nuclear%20bombs%20evokes%20much%20intrigue%20and%20concern%2C%20and%20at%20the%20same%20time%20serves%20as%20a%20sobering%20reminder%20of%20the%20inherent%20risks%20and%20consequences%20of%20nuclear%20proliferation.%20It%20underscores%20the%20need%20for%20robust%20safeguards%2C%20rigorous%20oversight%2C%20and%20international%20cooperation%20to%20prevent%20the%20unthinkable%20from%20happening%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708954140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-05%2Fnuclear-explosion-atom-bomb-generic_650x400_71462870420.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2F13-years-after-hiroshima-us-lost-3-nukes-one-70-times-stronger-5131308%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22However%2C%20experts%20have%20said%20that%20the%20risk%20of%20them%20causing%20a%20nuclear%20explosion%20is%20thought%20to%20be%20low.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2F