n-with-highest-score-shares-stunning-photos%2Farticleshow%2F108016073.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Japan's%20moon%20lander%20makes%20'miracle'%20response%20to%20signal%20from%20Earth%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708950840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F01%2F768x432%2Fskynews-slim-moon_6432556.jpg%3F20240125082007%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fjapans-moon-lander-makes-miracle-response-to-signal-from-earth-13081546%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Japan's%20first%20moon%20lander%20has%20responded%20to%20a%20signal%20from%20Earth%20in%20what%20has%20been%20hailed%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bmiracle%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20country's%20space%20agency.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A275%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fjapans-moon-lander-makes-miracle-response-to-signal-from-earth-13081546%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fjapans-moon-lander-makes-miracle-response-to-signal-from-earth-13081546%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fjapans-moon-lander-makes-miracle-response-to-signal-from-earth-13081546%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tiger%20Widows%20of%20Sundarbans%3A%20Judiciary%20Shows%20the%20Way%2C%20but%20Executive%20Loath%20to%20Follow%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26161045%2Fimage-2-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20October%2017%2C%202019%2C%20at%20around%203%3A30%20pm%2C%20Sambhu%20Mondal%20and%20Radhakanta%20Auliya%2C%20two%20fishermen%20from%20the%20Rajat%20Jubilee%20village%20of%20the%20Gosaba%20block%20of%20the%20Sundarbans%2C%20fell%20to%20a%20tiger%20attack.%20They%20were%20fishing%20in%20the%20waters%20of%20the%20Panchamukhani-II%20forest%20compartment%2C%20opposite%20Kalirchar%2C%20when%20the%20tiger%20attacked%20Sambhu.%20After%20Radhakanta%20rushed%20out%20to%20help%20him%2C%20the%20tiger%20let%20go%20of%20Sambhu%2C%20caught%20hold%20of%20Radhakanta%20and%20dragged%20him%20deep%20into%20the%20forests.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20surviving%20members%20of%20the%20fishing%20team%20carried%20Sambhu%20to%20the%20nearest%20primary%20health%20centre%20in%20Chhotomollakhali%20where%20he%20was%20declared%20dead.%20The%20remains%20of%20Radhakanta%20were%20never%20found.%20In%20the%20dense%20forests%20of%20the%20Sundarban%20delta%2C%20all%20signs%20of%20wildlife-depredation%20wash%20away%20into%20the%20sea%20when%20the%20high%20tides%20recede.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26160542%2Fimage-1-2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221028%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26160542%2Fimage-1-2.jpg%201028w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26160542%2Fimage-1-2-300x228.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26160542%2Fimage-1-2-1024x777.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698943%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22780%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFerry-boats%20on%20the%20Bidyadhari%20river%2C%20Gosaba%20block.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%20began%20the%20struggles%20of%20their%20wives%20%E2%80%93%20Sarojini%20Mondal%20and%20Saraswati%20Auliya%20%E2%80%93%20to%20obtain%20compensation.%20The%20death%20certificates%2C%20Panchayat-certifications%2C%20and%20police-investigation%20reports%20for%20both%20Sambhu%20and%20Radhakanta%20confirm%20that%20they%20died%20in%20a%20tiger-attack.%20The%20autopsy-report%20for%20Sambhu%20also%20states%20the%20same.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20Wildlife%20Protection%20Act%20(WLPA)%2C%201972%2C%20deaths%20caused%20by%20wildlife%20ought%20to%20be%20compensated.%20There%20have%20been%20several%20legal%20orders%20issued%20over%20the%20years%20by%20the%20forest%20department%20of%20West%20Bengal%2C%20specifying%20the%20amounts%20payable%20to%20wildlife-depredation%20victims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20of%20such%20orders%20was%20passed%20in%201979%2C%20when%20the%20amount%20payable%20to%20legal%20heirs%20in%20case%20of%20death%20due%20to%20animal%20attack%20was%20as%20little%20as%20Rs%202%2C500.%20However%2C%20the%20amount%20has%20increased%20over%20time.%20In%202015%20it%20was%20Rs%202.5%20lakhs.%20In%20the%20latest%20Government%20Orders%20passed%20in%202021%2C%20the%20state%20forest%20department%20has%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.westbengalforest.gov.in%2Fupload%2Fexgratia%2Fexgratia_order.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eincreased%20the%20compensation%20amount%20to%20Rs.%205%20lakhs%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20January%202020%2C%20Sarojini%20and%20Saraswati%20applied%20for%20compensation.%20During%20this%20period%2C%20they%20wrote%20to%20various%20forest%20authorities%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Range%20Officer%2C%20Sajnekhali%2C%20the%20Field%20Director%2C%20Sundarban%20Tiger%20Reserve%20(STR)%2C%20and%20even%20to%20the%20Principal%20Chief%20Conservator%20of%20Forests%20(PCCF)%2C%20who%20helms%20the%20state%20Forest%20Division.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20were%20given%20paralegal-assistance%20by%20the%20Sundarban%20Byaghrobidhoba%20Samiti%20(SBS)%20%E2%80%93%20a%20tiger-widows%E2%80%99%20collective%20from%20the%20Sundarbans.%20In%20popular%20Bengali%20parlance%2C%20wives%20of%20tiger-victims%20from%20the%20Sundarbans%20are%20called%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebyaghro-bidhoba%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20which%20translates%20to%20%E2%80%98tiger-widow%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20collective%2C%20operating%20since%202015%2C%20was%20formed%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20the%20Dakshinbanga%20Matsyajibi%20Forum%20(DMF)%20%E2%80%93%20a%20trade%20union%20of%20small-scale%20fish-workers%20from%20southern%20West%20Bengal.%20SBS%20provides%20paralegal-support%20and%20livelihood-training%20to%20wildlife-depredation-affected%20families%20from%20the%20Sundarbans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20organises%20legal%20awareness%20camps%2C%20legal%20aid%20clinics%20as%20well%20as%20assists%20people%20in%20writing%20letters%20to%20relevant%20authorities%20and%20facilitates%20meetings.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20myself%20am%2C%20an%20advocate%20by%20profession%2C%20has%20engaged%20extensively%20with%20the%20legal%20aid%20activities%20of%20the%20SBS%20Assisted%20by%20Kolkata-based%20lawyers%2C%20trade%20union-leaders%20of%20the%20DMF%2C%20and%20community-activists%20from%20places%20like%20Diamond%20Harbour%2C%20Gosaba%2C%20Lahiripur%20etc.%2C%20the%20SBS%20continues%20to%20provide%20paralegal%20services%20to%20wildlife-depredation%20affected%20people%20from%20the%20Sundarbans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26161045%2Fimage-2-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26161045%2Fimage-2-1.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26161045%2Fimage-2-1-300x193.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698948%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22659%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESome%20tiger%20widows%20from%20the%20Gosaba%20block%20in%20front%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Tiger%20Widows%20Community%20Centre%E2%80%99%20at%20Satjelia%2C%20with%20the%20SBS-banner%2C%20after%20a%20legal%20awareness%20camp%20on%2025.07.2023.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20March-April%202023%2C%20SBS%20helped%20Sarojini%2C%20Saraswati%20and%2023%20other%20tiger-widows%20from%20the%20Sundarbans%20to%20initiate%20proceedings%20before%20the%20West%20Bengal%20Commission%20for%20Women.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20commission%20forwarded%20their%20applications%20to%20the%20forest%20department.%20The%20subsequent%20departmental%20response%20was%20limited%20to%20the%20cases%20of%20Sambhu%2C%20Radhakanta%2C%20and%20four%20others%20who%20had%20lost%20their%20lives%20to%20tiger-attack%20between%202011%20and%202019.%20It%20stated%20that%20all%20those%20victims%20had%20illegally%20entered%20the%20forest%20when%20the%20attacks%20occurred.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20October%2C%202023%2C%20Sarojini%20and%20Saraswati%2C%20assisted%20by%20SBS%2C%20sent%20individual%20letters%20to%20the%20said%20forest%20authorities%2C%20once%20again%20requesting%20settlement%20of%20their%20claims.%20In%20response%2C%20the%20forest%20department%20denied%20their%20claims%20altogether%20on%20account%20of%20their%20husbands%E2%80%99%20alleged%20%E2%80%98illegal%E2%80%99%20forest-entry.%20Such%20reasoning%20is%20unsound.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Sundarban%20forests%20have%20been%20brought%20under%20the%20forest%20and%20wildlife%20conservancy%20regime%20on%20a%20piecemeal%20basis%20%E2%80%93%20starting%20from%20the%2019%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century%20and%20running%20up%20to%20the%2021%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Est%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESevere%20entry-restrictions%20imposed%20on%20the%20local%20fishers%20have%20harmed%20their%20livelihood%20prospects.%20Their%20rights%20have%20not%20been%20settled%20under%20the%20Indian%20Forest%20Act%2C%201927.%20No%20Gram%20Sabha%20consent%20was%20ever%20obtained%2C%20no%20livelihood-protection%20accorded%20and%20no%20settlement%20of%20forest%20rights%20was%20made%20under%20the%20WLPA%2C%201972%2C%20despite%20the%202006%20amendment%20which%20made%20such%20steps%20mandatory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20fish%20in%20the%20Sundarban-waters%2C%20fishers%20need%20a%20Boat%20License%20Certificate%20(a%20heritable%20and%20non-transferable%20document%20renewable%20annually)%20and%20a%20forest%20permit%2C%20which%20usually%20has%20a%2042-day%20validity%20period.%20The%20dubious%20nature%20of%20these%20documents%2C%20and%20administrative%20arbitrariness%20that%20prevails%20in%20this%20regard%20have%20been%20highlighted%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theindiaforum.in%2Farticle%2Flicence-kill-sundarbans%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20the%20past%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20only%20709%20BLCs%20operational%20in%20the%20tiger%20reserve%20area%2C%20according%20to%20information%20revealed%20by%20the%20field%20director%20of%20the%20reserve%20in%20response%20to%20an%20RTI%20filed%20by%20DMF.%20Other%20than%20these%2C%20there%20are%203%2C700%20BLCs%20active%20for%20the%20reserve%20forest%20areas%20of%20the%20Sundarban.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20an%20insignificant%20number%20when%20compared%20with%20the%202011%20census-data%20that%20points%20to%20fishing%20as%20a%20source%20of%20livelihood%20for%202-5%20lakh%20people%20in%20the%20Indian%20Sundarbans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProfessor%20Pranabes%20Sanyal%2C%20former%20FD%2C%20STR%2C%20had%20mentioned%20in%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dishaearth.org%2FTHE%2520SUNDARBANS%2520FISHERS.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Einterview%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20BLCs%20originate%20from%20boat%20registrations%20done%20between%201928%20and%201943.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20wives%20and%20dependants%20of%20wildlife-attack%20victims%20of%20the%20Sundarbans%2C%20this%20absurdity%20of%20the%20BLC-regime%20manifests%20patently.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Calcutta%20high%20court%2C%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EShantibala%20Naskar%20vs.%20the%20State%20of%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Others%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20held%20that%20compensation%20cannot%20be%20denied%20to%20the%20family-members%20of%20wildlife-attack%20victims%20on%20account%20of%20illegal%20forest-entry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20court%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F190574655%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edirected%20the%20authorities%20to%20pay%20Rs%205%20lakhs%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20compensation%20to%20the%20petitioner%20%E2%80%93%20a%20tiger-widow%20from%20the%20Sundarban-adjacent%20Kultali%20Gram%20Panchayat%20area.%20The%20forest%20authority%20tendered%20her%20the%20amount%20on%20October%2013%2C%202023.%20Ironically%2C%20Sarojini%20and%20Saraswati%E2%80%99s%20rejection%20letters%20are%20also%20dated%20the%20same.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAssisted%20by%20SBS%2C%20they%20wrote%20to%20the%20state-level%20forest%2C%20police%20and%20magisterial%20officers%2C%20highlighting%20this%20denial%20and%20discrimination.%20They%20also%20wrote%20to%20the%20state%20commission%20for%20women%2C%20before%20which%20they%20had%20filed%20individual%20proceedings%20earlier%20on.%20They%20visited%20the%20commission%E2%80%99s%20office%20in%20Kolkata%20personally%20in%20November%202023%2C%20seeking%2C%20in%20vain%2C%20counselling%20through%20its%20Pre-Litigation%20Counselling%20Cell.%20All%20subsequent%20efforts%20to%20contact%20the%20commission%20through%20phone-calls%20and%C2%A0%20emails%20have%20not%20yielded%20any%20results.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20444px)%2085vw%2C%20444px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26161159%2Fimage-3-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22444%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26161159%2Fimage-3-1.jpg%20444w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26161159%2Fimage-3-1-288x300.jpg%20288w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698949%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22462%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%5BL-R%5D%20Saraswati%20Auliya%20and%20Sarojini%20Mondal%20at%20the%20WB%20Commission%20for%20Women%20office%2C%2002.11.2023.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20November%2017%2C%202023%2C%20Sarojini%20and%20Saraswati%20moved%20the%20court%20with%20their%20writ%20petitions.%20The%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20heard%20their%20cases%20and%20directed%20the%20authorities%20to%20pay%20Rs%205%20lakhs%20to%20both%20of%20them%2C%20reiterating%20its%20earlier%20position%20that%20illegal%20forest-entry%20cannot%20be%20used%20as%20a%20ground%20for%20denial%20of%20compensation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20further%20rounds%20of%20scrutiny%20by%20the%20reserve%20authorities%20and%20the%20bank%2C%20they%20received%20the%20money%20on%20February%207%2C%202024.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20cannot%20be%20said%20that%20the%20legal%20injuries%20faced%20by%20Sarojini%20and%20Saraswati%20have%20all%20been%20aptly%20addressed.%20Both%20Sambhu%20and%20Radhakanta%20were%20policy-holders%20with%20the%20publicly%20owned%20United%20India%20Insurance%20Company%20(UII)%2C%20with%20their%20wives%20as%20nominees.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20UII%20continues%20to%20deny%20their%20insurance%20claims%20till%20date%20on%20grounds%20of%20alleged%20illegal%20forest-entry.%20The%20forest%20permit%20of%20the%20fishing%20team%20had%20expired%20by%203%20days%20on%20the%20date%20of%20the%20tiger-attack.%20But%20the%20team%20leader%20%E2%80%93%20Jagabandhu%20Bauliya%20%E2%80%93%20had%20subsequently%20paid%20the%20necessary%20fine%20to%20the%20forest%20department.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20May%202022%2C%20nearly%20two%20years%20after%20Jagabandhu%20passed%20away%2C%20Sarojini%20requested%20the%20forest%20department%20in%20writing%20for%20a%20copy%20of%20this%20receipt.%20The%20department%20is%20yet%20to%20respond.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESarojini%20and%20Saraswati%20were%20never%20opaque%20about%20this%20predicament.%20They%20have%20written%20to%20UII%20as%20well%20as%20all%20the%20relevant%20forest%2C%20police%20and%20civil-administration%20authorities.%20Yet%2C%20they%20continue%20to%20be%20denied%20their%20rightful%20insurance%20claims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20the%20Postmaster%20of%20the%20Sadhupur%20post%20office%20had%20initially%20refused%20to%20give%20Sarojini%20the%20money%20that%20her%20husband%20had%20in%20his%20postal%20account%20at%20the%20time%20of%20his%20death%2C%20saying%20that%20when%20someone%20dies%2C%20the%20money%20in%20their%20account%20becomes%20the%20government%E2%80%99s.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20tiger-widows%2C%20unlike%20Sarojini%20and%20Saraswati%2C%20do%20not%20possess%20documents%20that%20establish%20tiger-attack%20as%20the%20cause%20of%20their%20husbands%E2%80%99%20deaths.%20Efforts%20to%20procure%20the%20same%20are%20resisted%20by%20the%20forest%2C%20police%20and%20civic%20authorities%2C%20often%20through%20downright%20hostility.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26161404%2Fimage-4-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26161404%2Fimage-4-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26161404%2Fimage-4-1-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26161404%2Fimage-4-1-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698950%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAn%20S.B.S.%20delegation%20of%20tiger%20widows%20and%20activists%20at%20the%20block%20administrative%20office%20of%20Gosaba%2C%2021.08.2023.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECompensation%20and%20insurance%20are%20not%20the%20only%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eex-gratia%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20rights%20available%20to%20family-members%20of%20wildlife%20attack%20victims%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20As%20per%20the%20West%20Bengal%20Scheme%20for%20Rehabilitation%20by%20Providing%20Employment%20Assistance%2C%202023%2C%20one%20member%20from%20each%20such%20family%20is%20also%20entitled%20to%20contractual%20employment%20with%20the%20forest%20department.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20as%20ground-level%20experiences%20from%20the%20Sundarbans%20reveal%2C%20these%20laws%20remain%20scantly%20implemented.%20Despite%20these%20mounting%20odds%2C%20SBS%2C%20as%20a%20community-based%20collective%2C%20continues%20to%20fight%20for%20the%20legal%20rights%20of%20human-wildlife%20conflict-victims%20from%20the%20Sundarbans.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708950540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26161045%2Fimage-2-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ftiger-widows-of-sundarbans-judiciary-shows-the-way-executive-loath-to-follow%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20recent%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20judgments%20outline%20the%20struggles%20faced%20by%20the%20family%20members%20of%20tiger-attack%20victims%20in%20securing%20their%20legal%20rights.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ftiger-widows-of-sundarbans-judiciary-shows-the-way-executive-loath-to-follow%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'No%20Stay%2C%20Arrest%20Shahjahan%2C'%20Says%20Calcutta%20HC%3B%20Sandeshkhali%20Remains%20on%20the%20Boil%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26164522%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-23-at-9.43.40-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKolkata%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20unrest%20at%20Sandeshkhali%20reached%20the%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20on%20February%2026%2C%20with%20a%20division%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20T.S.%20Sivagnanam%20noting%20that%20there%20is%20no%20stay%20on%20the%20arrest%20of%20absconding%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20%E2%80%93%20North%2024-Parganas%20zilla%20parishad%E2%80%99s%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArrest%20him.%20Complaints%20were%20made%20as%20many%20as%20four%20years%20ago%2C%20why%20was%20he%20not%20arrested%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20the%20bench%2C%20which%20also%20comprised%20Justice%20Hiranmay%20Bhattacharya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%2C%20which%20has%20taken%20suo%20motu%20cognisance%20of%20the%20allegations%20of%20systemic%20sexual%20harassment%20and%20intimidation%20at%20Sandeshkhali%20by%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leaders%2C%20clarified%20that%20there%20was%20no%20stay%20on%20the%20arrest%20of%20Shahjahan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETMC%20supremo%20Mamata%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20nephew%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%20member%20of%20parliament%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20had%20earlier%20said%20that%20police%20could%20not%20arrest%20Shahjahan%20because%20of%20a%20stay%20on%20his%20arrest%20by%20the%20courts.%20From%20various%20quarters%2C%20allegations%20had%20been%20coming%20in%20that%20the%20police%20were%20shielding%20the%20TMC%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Will%20be%20arrested%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImmediately%20after%20the%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20order%2C%20the%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20spokesperson%20Kunal%20Ghosh%20said%20on%20social%20media%20that%20Shahjahan%20will%20be%20%E2%80%9Carrested%20in%20seven%20days.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETMC%20%E2%80%93%20under%20fire%20over%20the%20claims%20at%20Sandeshkhali%20%E2%80%93%20has%20announced%20a%20rally%20at%20Kolkata%E2%80%99s%20iconic%20Brigade%20Parade%20grounds%20on%20March%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommunist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20MP%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Bikash%20Ranjan%20Bhattacharya%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CTMC%E2%80%99s%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%20is%20entirely%20in%20the%20shelter%20of%20the%20state%20police.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20has%20ordered%20a%20stay%20of%20three%20months%20on%20the%20state%20CID%E2%80%99s%20case%20against%20ABP%20Ananda%20vice-president%20and%20journalist%20Suman%20De.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20anchor%20has%20repeatedly%20apologised%20for%20the%20false%20news%20that%20was%20aired.%20While%20it%20may%20be%20probed%20as%20to%20why%20this%20news%20was%20aired%2C%20the%20charges%20against%20him%20are%20not%20acceptable%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Justice%20Kaushik%20Chanda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETMC%20leader%20held%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Sandeshkhali%20itself%2C%20there%20has%20been%20heavy%20police%20and%20security%20force%20presence%20at%20the%20houses%20of%20TMC%20leaders%2C%20which%20are%20often%20being%20stormed%20by%20angry%20villagers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20morning%20of%20February%2026%2C%20villagers%20attacked%20the%20house%20of%20a%20TMC%20leader%20from%20Bermajur%2C%20Shankar%20Sardar.%20Sarkar%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Gram%20Panchayat.%20Local%20women%20alleged%20that%20Shankar%20used%20guns%20to%20intimidate%20them%20often%20and%20is%20close%20to%20TMC%20ministers.%20Locals%20alleged%20that%20along%20with%20another%20strongman%2C%20Tapan%20Sardar%2C%20Shankar%20used%20to%20also%20take%20away%20the%20daily%20wages%20earned%20by%20labourers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20weekend%2C%20angry%20villagers%20had%20also%20stormed%20the%20house%20of%20local%20heavyweight%20Ajit%20Maity.%20Maity%20fled%20and%20took%20shelter%20at%20a%20civic%20volunteer%E2%80%99s%20house.%20Police%20eventually%20took%20him%20into%20custody.%20Climbing%20onto%20a%20police%20jeep%2C%20Maity%20told%20reporters%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20a%20BJP%20worker%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20I%20joined%20TMC%20in%202019.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20these%20earlier%20complaints%20against%20me%20are.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVillagers%20are%20resolute%20that%20Maity%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20strong-arming%20tactics%20had%20been%20in%20place%20even%20before.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20has%20always%20tortured%20the%20poor.%20He%20took%20our%20land%20earlier%20as%20well.%20Greed%20drove%20him%20to%20the%20TMC%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20one%20Nirmala%20Sardar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETMC%20ministers%20visit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20leaders%20of%20a%20beleaguered%20TMC%20held%20public%20meetings%20at%20Sandeshkhali.%20Villagers%2C%20armed%20with%20brooms%20and%20sticks%2C%20stopped%20Sujit%20Bose%20and%20Partha%20Bhowmick%20on%20the%20tracks.%20The%20two%20had%20to%20hold%20their%20meeting%20at%20the%20Bermajur%20School.%20With%20Ajit%20Maity%20behind%20bars%2C%20Bose%20and%20Bhowmik%20announced%20that%20Haladhar%20Ari%20and%20Shaktipada%20Raut%20would%20take%20over%20temporary%20charge%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20local%20wing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20irrigation%20minister%20Bhowmick%20claimed%20the%20allegations%20of%20wrongdoing%20were%20not%20exactly%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPerhaps%20some%20people%20have%20been%20mentally%20tortured%20but%20never%20physically.%20We%20will%20not%20spare%20anyone%20who%20has%20stolen%20land%20in%20the%20Bengal%20ruled%20by%20Didi%20%5BCM%20Mamata%20Banerjee%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhowmick%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20ministers%20then%20participated%20in%20a%20kirtan%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20morning%2C%20harvested%20grains%20stored%20at%20the%20newly%20appointed%20Panchayat%20Samiti%20chief%20Haladhar%20Ari%E2%80%99s%20house%20was%20set%20on%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26164749%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-24-at-2.46.07-PM-1024x558.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26164749%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-24-at-2.46.07-PM-1024x558.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26164749%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-24-at-2.46.07-PM-300x163.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26164749%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-24-at-2.46.07-PM.jpeg%201080w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698960%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22458%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20CPIM%20team%20interacts%20with%20Sandeshkhali%20villagers.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVillagers%20have%20also%20alleged%20that%20Section%20144%20of%20the%20CrPC%20is%20being%20misused%20by%20police%20to%20ensure%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20gather.