estinian%20President%20Mahmoud%20Abbas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EShtayyeh%20added%20that%20he%20resigned%20last%20Tuesday%20but%20handed%20in%20the%20written%20resignation%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20the%20prime%20minister%20said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CI%20submit%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20to%20Mr.%20President%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shtayyeh%20said.%20He%20added%20that%20it%20came%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdevelopments%20related%20to%20the%20aggression%20against%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20and%20the%20escalation%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20and%20Jerusalem.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EShtayyeh%20added%20that%20he%20was%20resigning%20to%20allow%20Palestinians%20to%20form%20a%20broad%20consensus%20among%20Palestinians%20about%20political%20arrangements%20amid%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20war%20against%20Hamas%2C%20a%20Palestinian%20militant%20group%2C%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20US%20has%20been%20pressuring%20Abbas%20to%20shake%20up%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%2C%20which%20rules%20parts%20of%20the%20occupied%20West%20Bank.%20This%20comes%20amid%20international%20efforts%20to%20stop%20the%20war%20and%20work%20toward%20a%20political%20structure%20to%20govern%20Gaza%20afterward.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAbbas%20has%20yet%20to%20accept%20the%20resignation%2C%20and%20he%20may%20ask%20the%20Palestinian%20prime%20minister%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20role%20until%20a%20replacement%20is%20found.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20the%20Cabinet%2C%20Shtayyeh%20said%20the%20next%20stage%20would%20%E2%80%9Crequire%20new%20governmental%20and%20political%20arrangements%20that%20take%20into%20account%20the%20emerging%20reality%20in%20the%