h%20Injured%20at%20Khanauri%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26152436%2F567702e5-2fa3-47cc-a5f8-2ca0f5bf3c75.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJalandhar%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EFor%20the%20family%20of%20Pritpal%20Singh%2C%20February%2024%20was%20a%20day%20of%20respite%20as%20their%20only%20son%20was%20finally%20shifted%20to%20the%20Post%20Graduate%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Education%20and%20Research%20(PGI)%20Chandigarh%20from%20the%20restricted%20environment%20of%20PGI%20Rohtak%2C%20Haryana%20where%20he%20was%20admitted%20for%20multiple%20fractures%20in%20his%20leg%2C%20nose%20and%20jaw%20and%20severe%20injuries%20on%20his%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPritpal%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Nawangaon%20village%20of%20Moonak%20sub-division%2C%20Sangrur%20district%2C%20was%20reportedly%20picked%20up%20by%20the%20Haryana%20Police%20on%20February%2021%20from%20Khanauri%20border%2C%20on%20the%20Punjab%20side.%20He%20was%20allegedly%20put%20in%20a%20gunny%20bag%20and%20beaten%20mercilessly%20when%20he%20serving%20langar.%20Incidentally%2C%20Sangrur%20is%20the%20home%20turf%20of%20Punjab%20chief%20minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20only%20when%20he%20was%20being%20taken%20to%20a%20hospital%20in%20an%20ambulance%20that%20Pritpal%20managed%20to%20call%20his%20parents%20and%20in%20broken%20sentences%20tell%20them%20what%20had%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakhvir%20Kaur%2C%20Pritpal%E2%80%99s%20mother%20who%20was%20at%20PGI%20Chandigarh%20for%20her%20son%E2%80%99s%20surgery%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20on%20February%2021%2C%20Pritpal%20was%20at%20Khanauri%20border%20inside%20Punjabi%20territory%2C%20when%20suddenly%20the%20Haryana%20Police%20started%20throwing%20tear%20gas%20shells%20at%20the%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20that%20chaos%2C%20when%20tear%20gas%20shells%20fell%20and%20farmers%20started%20running%20to%20save%20themselves%2C%20the%20Haryana%20Police%20crossed%20the%20Khanauri%20border%20and%20picked%20up%20my%20son.%20They%20put%20him%20in%20a%20sack%20and%20beat%20up%20mercilessly%20with%20sticks%20and%20rods%20till%20he%20became%20unconscious.%20Somehow%2C%20the%20almighty%20saved%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20how%20they%20found%20out%20about%20what%20happened%2C%20Lakhvir%20said%20that%20Pritpal%20used%20to%20carry%20two%20mobile%20phones.%20While%20one%20was%20snatched%20by%20the%20Haryana%20Police%2C%20the%20second%20somehow%20remained%20in%20one%20of%20his%20pockets.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20beating%20my%20son%2C%20they%20had%20thrown%20him%20in%20the%20fields%20but%20later%20when%20they%20saw%20his%20condition%2C%20they%20took%20him%20to%20a%20private%20hospital%20in%20Narwana%2C%20Haryana.%20When%20Pritpal%20was%20being%20taken%20to%20the%20hospital%20in%20the%20ambulance%20at%20around%201%3A30%20pm%2C%20he%20called%20up%20and%20informed%20us%20that%20he%20had%20been%20taken%20to%20Narwana%20in%20Jind%20district%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESobbing%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20moment%20we%20learnt%20about%20Pritpal%E2%80%99s%20condition%2C%20we%20informed%20some%20of%20our%20relatives%20in%20Haryana.%20They%20managed%20to%20chase%20the%20ambulance%2C%20which%20initially%20took%20him%20to%20a%20hospital%20in%20Narwana.%20We%20also%20immediately%20rushed%20from%20Sangrur.%20But%20seeing%20his%20condition%2C%20the%20doctors%20referred%20my%20son%20to%20PGI%20Rohtak%2C%20where%20he%20remained%20for%20three%20days.%20My%20son%20went%20through%20hell%20during%20this%20period.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakhvir%20said%20that%20at%20PGI%20Rohtak%2C%20the%20Haryana%20Police%20and%20some%20men%20in%20civil%20clothes%20tracked%20them%2024%C3%977.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20PGI%20Rohtak%2C%20Haryana%20Police%20were%20deployed%20outside%20my%20son%E2%80%99s%20room.%20Whenever%20we%20would%20talk%20or%20attend%20to%20any%20phone%20call%2C%20the%20men%20in%20civil%20dress%20used%20to%20follow%20us.%20They%20kept%20tracking%20us%20throughout%20the%20day%20and%20night.%20Even%20if%20we%20used%20to%20go%20out%20to%20take%20a%20call%2C%20they%20used%20to%20follow%20us%20and%20would%20try%20to%20listen%20to%20our%20conversation.%20They%20even%20threatened%20us%20against%20talking%20to%20the%20media.%20We%20felt%20helpless%20and%20wanted%20to%20reach%20Punjab%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20fear.%20We%20felt%20unsafe%20and%20disturbed%20at%20PGI%20Rohtak.%20Whenever%20my%20son%20regained%20consciousness%2C%20he%20would%20plead%20us%20to%20take%20him%20to%20Punjab.%20The%20Haryana%20Police%20took%20Pritpal%20to%20PGI%20Rohtak%20so%20that%20we%20could%20not%20be%20there.%20Had%20senior%20farmers%E2%80%99%20union%20leader%20Baldev%20Singh%20Sirsa%20not%20helped%20us%2C%20we%20would%20have%20been%20ruined.%20He%20remained%20in%20touch%20with%20us%20and%20expedited%20Pritpal%E2%80%99s%20return%20to%20Punjab%2C%E2%80%9D%20Lakhvir%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26152624%2FIMG_4150.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26152624%2FIMG_4150.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26152624%2FIMG_4150-300x187.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26152624%2FIMG_4150-1024x637.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698917%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22747%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EKisan%20Mazdoor%20Morcha%20coordinator%20Sarvan%20Singh%20Pandher%20and%20senior%20farmer%20union%20leader%20Baldev%20Singh%20Sirsa%20along%20with%20Pritpal%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20parents%20at%20PGI%20Chandigarh%20on%20Sunday.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors%20conducted%20Pritpal%E2%80%99s%20surgery%20on%20Sunday.%20It%20started%20at%20around%20noon%20and%20went%20on%20till%206%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPritpal%E2%80%99s%20return%20to%20Punjab%20became%20possible%20only%20when%20farmers%E2%80%99%20unions%20brought%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20Mann%20government.%20It%20was%20then%20that%20the%20Punjab%20chief%20secretary%2C%20Anurag%20Verma%2C%20shot%20off%20a%20letter%20to%20Haryana%20chief%20secretary%20Sanjeev%20Kaushal%20requesting%20him%20to%20send%20Pritpal%20Singh%20back%20for%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20many%20farmers%20who%20witnessed%20the%20chaos%20of%20February%2021%20had%20been%20claiming%20that%20it%20was%20men%20in%20civil%20clothes%20who%20picked%20up%20some%20youth%20from%20the%20Khanauri%20border%2C%20took%20them%20to%20Haryana%20and%20beat%20them%20mercilessly.%20They%20also%20said%20that%20it%20was%20the%20Haryana%20Police%20which%20shielded%20these%20men%20in%20civil%20clothes%20while%20they%20ransacked%20everything%2C%20abused%20farmers%20and%20beat%20them%20with%20batons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20to%20counter%20these%20charges%2C%20the%20Haryana%20Police%20on%20February%2024%20shared%20a%20map%20with%20the%20media%20and%20came%20along%20with%20a%20team%20of%20revenue%20officials%20to%20claim%20that%20the%20February%2021%20operation%20against%20the%20farmers%20was%20within%20their%20own%20jurisdiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20(DSP)%20Narwana%20Amit%20Kumar%20Bhatia%2C%20who%20addressed%20the%20media%20earlier%2C%20was%20not%20available%20for%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20top%20official%20also%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20right%20on%20the%20land%20towards%20Punjab%20on%201965%20feet%20(600%20meters)%20from%20the%20point%20of%20our%20barricades%20at%20Data%20Singhwala%20village.%20The%20farmers%20occupy%2012%20more%20acres%20of%20our%20territory%20along%20Punjab%2C%20which%20we%20have%20reported%20to%20the%20Punjab%20authorities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20%3Cem%3Eamritdhari%3C%2Fem%3E%20(baptised)%20Sikh%2C%20Pritpal%20Singh%20was%20part%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Chalo%20protest%20which%20is%20being%20led%20by%20the%20Samyukt%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(nonpolitical)%20and%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Morcha%20(KMM)%20led%20by%20Jagjit%20Singh%20Dallewal%20and%20Sarvan%20Singh%20Pandher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20farmers%20had%20given%20a%20call%20for%20the%20Delhi%20Chalo%20morcha%20on%20February%2013.%20Since%20the%20Haryana%20police%20sealed%20the%20borders%20leading%20to%20Delhi%2C%20the%20farmers%20have%20been%20camping%20at%20Punjab-Haryana%E2%80%99s%20Shambhu%20and%20Khanauri%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPunjab%20BJP%20mum%20but%20Amarinder%20terms%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20actions%20%E2%80%98barbaric%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Punjab%20chief%20minister%20Amarinder%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20now%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20Haryana%20Police%20and%20termed%20its%20actions%20against%20the%20farmers%20%E2%80%98barbaric%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20strongly%20condemn%20the%20barbaric%20act%20of%20violence%20committed%20by%20the%20Haryana%20Police%20on%20our%20young%20farmer%20Pritpal%20Singh.%20I%20urge%20Haryana%20CM%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20to%20take%20strict%20action%20against%20the%20policemen%20who%20are%20guilty%20of%20badly%20beating%20up%20an%20unarmed%20youngster%20who%20was%20just%20serving%20langar%20to%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20BJP%20Punjab%20President%20Sunil%20Jakhar%20expressed%20condolences%20over%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-protest-haryana-police-shubhkaran-singh%5C%22%3Etragic%20death%20of%2022-year-old%20Shubhkaran%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20demanded%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20into%20the%20matter.%20%E2%80%9CI%20demand%20the%20strictest%20action%20against%20those%20responsible%20to%20prevent%20the%20recurrence%20of%20such%20a%20mishap%2C%20because%20there%20are%20thousands%20of%20our%20Shubhkarans%20at%20protest%20sites%20even%20today.%20Both%20sides%20must%20remember%2C%20every%20life%20matters%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rest%20of%20the%20BJP%20Punjab%20leadership%20is%20maintaining%20a%20silence%20over%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20considering%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20which%20are%20just%20around%20the%20corner.%20Last%20time%20during%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20in%202020-2021%2C%20BJP%20leaders%20in%20Punjab%20had%20to%20face%20widespread%20protests%2C%20wiping%20out%20their%20political%20ground%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20(SAD)%2C%20which%20had%20snapped%20ties%20with%20its%20ally%20the%20BJP%20during%20the%20previous%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%2C%20is%20shying%20away%20from%20directly%20naming%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20any%20of%20its%20statements.%20SAD%20is%20squarely%20blaming%20chief%20minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20for%20the%20attacks%20on%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20SAD%20and%20the%20BJP%20were%20planning%20an%20alliance%20before%20the%20general%20elections%202024%2C%20which%20is%20stalled%20as%20of%20now.%20It%20was%20only%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20government%20and%20Punjab%20Congress%20leadership%20which%20was%20questioning%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20Haryana%20government%20for%20attacking%20the%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFarmers%E2%80%99%20union%20leaders%20meet%20Pritpal%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20family%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20delegation%20of%20the%20KMM%20led%20by%20Sarvan%20Singh%20Pandher%2C%20Amarjit%20Singh%20Mohri%2C%20Satnam%20Singh%20Sahni%20and%20others%20met%20Pritpal%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20family%20at%20PGI%20Chandigarh%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20Sarvan%20Singh%20Pandher%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20already%20raised%20this%20issue%20in%20our%20press%20conference%20on%20February%2021%20evening%20that%20four%20to%20five%20youths%20were%20picked%20up%20by%20Haryana%20Police.%20Pritpal%20Singh%20has%20been%20brought%20to%20PGI%20Chandigarh%2C%20where%20he%20will%20get%20the%20best%20treatment%20and%20recover%20soon.%20The%20other%20four%20injured%20youth%20are%20being%20treated%20at%20Government%20Rajindra%20Hospital%2C%20Patiala.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandher%20lashed%20out%20at%20Mann%20and%20said%20that%20he%20had%20assured%20farmers%20he%20would%20file%20an%20FIR%20against%20Haryana%20chief%20minister%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%2C%20home%20minister%20Anil%20Vij%20and%20police%20under%20Section%20356%20IPC%20but%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20done%20anything%20so%20far.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20apparent%20that%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20was%20acting%20under%20pressure%20from%20the%20Central%20government.%20That%20is%20why%20he%20has%20not%20registered%20any%20FIR%20against%20the%20Haryana%20Police.%20We%20demand%20justice%20for%20our%20youth%20and%20protests%20will%20continue%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26152536%2F4e477551-5819-4af7-bb24-325ebfddf96b.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26152536%2F4e477551-5819-4af7-bb24-325ebfddf96b.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26152536%2F4e