ely%2C%20indicates%20a%20growing%20concern.%20This%20sentiment%20suggests%20potential%20challenges%20ahead%2C%20as%20rising%20prices%20can%20erode%20purchasing%20power%2C%20leading%20to%20reduced%20consumer%20spending.%20Such%20a%20scenario%20could%20dampen%20economic%20growth%20and%20exacerbate%20inflationary%20pressures%2C%20impacting%20overall%20economic%20stability.%20Addressing%20these%20concerns%20is%20crucial%20to%20maintaining%20consumer%20confidence%2C%20sustaining%20economic%20growth%2C%20and%20ensuring%20affordability%20for%20essential%20goods%20and%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBelow%20we%20discuss%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20RBI%20Consumer%20Survey%20data%20which%20provides%20a%20direct%20alignment%20with%20the%20household%20consumption%20data%20released%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEvidence%20for%20a%20K-shaped%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20closer%20look%20at%20the%20RBI%E2%80%99s%20Consumer%20Survey%20time-series%20data%20reveals%20glaring%20inequality%20staring%20at%20the%20face%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20sluggish%20economic%20growth%20story.%20The%20K-shaped%20growth%20pattern%20becomes%20more%20evident%20when%20one%20carefully%20aligns%20the%20consumer%20confidence%20and%20perception%20data%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fauthor%2F310387%2Fdeepanshu-mohan%5C%22%3Ewith%20other%20macroeconomic%20realities%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20real%20wages%2C%20consumption%20patterns%2C%20employment%20growth%2C%20household%20debt%20and%20a%20widening%20credit-GDP%20gap%20(creating%20excess%20liquidity%20concerns%20for%20the%20central%20bank).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20537px)%2085vw%2C%20537px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26113326%2FK4.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22537%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26113326%2FK4.png%20880w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26113326%2FK4-300x180.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698864%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22322%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESource%3A%20Author%E2%80%99s%20Calculations%20from%20RBI%20Consumer%20Survey%20(February%2C%202024)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20January%202023%20to%20November%202023%2C%20a%20downward%20trend%20in%20the%20perception%20of%20the%20general%20economic%20situation%20is%20evident%20amongst%20Indians%20(see%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frbidocs.rbi.org.in%2Frdocs%2FPublications%2FPDFs%2FCCSJAN202478714E90EB494A0983DC279398C89831.PDF%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20more%20detailed%20analysis).%20Over%20this%20period%2C%20the%20percentage%20of%20individuals%20perceiving%20a%20decrease%20in%20the%20general%20economic%20condition%20consistently%20exceeds%20those%20reporting%20an%20increase%20or%20maintaining%20the%20same%20perception.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20prolonged%20pattern%20suggests%20a%20prevailing%20atmosphere%20of%20pessimism%20or%20economic%20uncertainty%2C%20reflecting%20broader%20concerns%20of%20adverse%20public%20sentiments%20and%20dis-confidence%20in%20economic%20prospects%20amongst%20certain%20economic%20groups%2C%20which%2C%20as%20crisis%20economists%20explain%2C%20have%20their%20own%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26rct%3Dj%26q%3D%26esrc%3Ds%26source%3Dweb%26cd%3D%26cad%3Drja%26uact%3D8%26ved%3D2ahUKEwjB0oj6xsCEAxUUzTgGHTkUD2YQFnoECBAQAQ%26url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.investopedia.com%252Fterms%252Fm%252Fmultiplier.asp%26usg%3DAOvVaw3r57sG0UlM4FtbVoixIzSm%26opi%3D89978449%5C%22%3Emultiplier%20effect%3C%2Fa%3E%20(amplifying%20its%20effect%20on%20other%20aggregates)%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20RBI%20data%2C%20in%20January%202024%2C%20a%20temporal%20shift%20in%20perception%20compared%20to%20previous%20months%20is%20also%20evident%20for%20some%20income%20brackets%2C%20with%20a%20notable%20increase%20in%20the%20percentage%20of%20people%20perceiving%20an%20improvement%20in%20the%20economic%20situation%2C%20rising%20from%2033.1%25%20to%2037.5%25.%20Conversely%2C%20the%20percentage%20of%20individuals%20perceiving%20a%20decrease%20in%20the%20economic%20situation%20has%20decreased%2C%20dropping%20from%2044.4%25%20to%2040.2%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chart%20below%20shows%20quite%20clear%20evidence%20of%20what%20has%20been%20perceived%20as%20a%20K-shaped%20economic%20recovery%20for%20India%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20in%20the%20post%20Covid%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20545px)%2085vw%2C%20545px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26113514%2FK5.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22545%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26113514%2FK5.png%20938w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26113514%2FK5-300x181.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698865%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22329%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20perception%20of%20the%20general%20economic%20situation%20varies%20significantly%20across%20different%20income%20brackets%2C%20as%20revealed%20by%20the%20provided%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20individuals%20earning%20less%20than%20Rs%205%2C000%2C%20a%20concerning%20trend%20emerges%2C%20with%20the%20majority%20(62%25)%20perceiving%20a%20monthly%20worsening%20economic%20situation.%20In%20contrast%2C%20only%2021%25%20report%20an%20improvement.%20This%20persistent%20negative%20perception%20suggests%20ongoing%20financial%20strain%20or%20challenges%20within%20this%20income%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20for%20those%20earning%20between%20Rs%205%2C000%20and%20%26lt%3BRs%2010%2C000%2C%20while%20there%20is%20a%20slightly%20higher%20percentage%20(28%25)%20reporting%20an%20improvement%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20income%20bracket%2C%20a%20significant%20portion%20(52%25)%20still%20perceives%20a%20worsening%20economic%20situation%20monthly.%20This%20indicates%20an%20overall%20negative%20outlook%20despite%20some%20improvement%20perception.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoving%20up%20the%20income%20scale%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000-%26lt%3BRs%2025%2C000%2C%20the%20data%20reflects%20a%20notable%20divide.%20While%2032%25%20report%20an%20improvement%2C%20a%20considerable%2044%25%20perceive%20a%20worsening%20economic%20situation%20monthly.%20This%20suggests%20persistent%20challenges%20despite%20some%20improvements%20within%20this%20income%20range.%20In%20the%20Rs%2025%2C000-%26lt%3BRs%2050%2C000%20bracket%2C%20perceptions%20are%20more%20balanced%2C%20with%2038%25%20reporting%20improvement%20and%20an%20equal%20percentage%20reporting%20worsening%20condition%20monthly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20individuals%20earning%20between%20Rs%2050%2C000%20and%20%26lt%3BRs%201%20lakh%2C%20a%20majority%20(47%25)%20perceive%20an%20improvement%20monthly%2C%20signalling%20a%20generally%20positive%20outlook.%20However%2C%20concerns%20persist%20as%2030%25%20still%20perceive%20a%20worsening%20economic%20situation%2C%20highlighting%20ongoing%20issues%20despite%20overall%20improvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20the%20highest%20income%20bracket%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%20and%20above%20demonstrates%20the%20most%20positive%20perception%2C%20with%2055%25%20reporting%20an%20improvement%20monthly.%20Only%2025%25%20of%20individuals%20in%20this%20group%20perceive%20a%20worsening%20economic%20situation%2C%20indicating%20a%20largely%20optimistic%20outlook%20among%20higher-income%20earners.%20See%20below%20for%20a%20macro-reality%20check%20on%20how%20real%20incomes%20have%20stagnated%20across%20income%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20540px)%2085vw%2C%20540px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F26115006%2FK6.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22540