onomy%2Fgrowing-evidence-of-a-vanishing-middle-class-struggling-low-income-class-in-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MEA%20Reiterates%20it%20Is%20Pursuing%20Discharge%20of%20Indians%20Lured%20Into%20Russian%20Army%20as%20More%20Reports%20Emerge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F04230638%2FEffect-12.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20With%20more%20cases%20of%20Indians%20being%20reportedly%20conned%20into%20joining%20the%20fight%20on%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20behalf%20in%20Ukraine%20coming%20to%20the%20fore%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20reiterated%20that%20it%20has%20taken%20up%20%E2%80%9Ceach%20and%20every%E2%80%9D%20case%20with%20Russian%20authorities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%2C%20there%20were%20reports%20suggesting%20that%20over%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fover-100-indians-recruited-as-army-helpers-in-russia-report%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E100%20Indian%20nationals%20may%20have%20been%20recruited%20as%20security%20helpers%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0by%20the%20Russian%20Army.%20Many%20alleged%20that%20they%20were%20coerced%20into%20combat%20areas%20alongside%20Russian%20forces%2C%20despite%20assurances%20that%20they%20would%20not%20be%20deployed%20in%20active%20conflict%20zones.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20it%20was%20reported%20that%20a%2023-year-old%20man%20from%20Gujarat%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2F23-year-old-indian-national-hired-as-security-helper-in-russia-killed-in-war-zone%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewas%20killed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20a%20Ukrainian%20air%20strike%20in%20the%20Donetsk%20region%20on%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20border%20on%20February%2021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fjob-fraud-kashmiri-conned-into-fighting-for-russian-army-against-ukraine%2Fcid%2F2002938%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20new%20media%20report%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Students%20Association%20claimed%20that%20two%20men%20from%20Kashmir%20were%20fraudulently%20lured%20to%20fight%20for%20the%20Russian%20army%20in%20Ukraine.%20While%20one%20of%20them%20has%20been%20injured%2C%20another%20is%20reportedly%20missing.%20They%20claimed%20to%20have%20written%20to%20external%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%2C%20urging%20for%20the%20repatriation%20of%20the%20two%20men.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fpress-releases.htm%3Fdtl%2F37661%2FMedia%2Breports%2Bregarding%2BIndian%2Bnationals%2Bseeking%2Bdischarge%2Bfrom%2Bthe%2BRussian%2BArmy%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20MEA%20on%20Monday%20claimed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20these%20were%20%E2%80%9Cinaccurate%E2%80%9D%20reports%20in%20the%20media.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CEach%20and%20every%20such%20case%20brought%20to%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%20in%20Moscow%20has%20been%20strongly%20taken%20up%20with%20the%20Russian%20authorities%20and%20those%20brought%20to%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20Ministry%20have%20been%20taken%20up%20with%20the%20Russian%20Embassy%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20Several%20Indians%20have%20already%20been%20discharged%20as%20a%20result%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20MEA%20press%20note.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20MEA%20added%20that%20it%20was%20actively%20pursuing%20all%20cases%20of%20Indian%20nationals%20for%20an%20early%20discharge%20from%20the%20Russian%20army%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmatter%20of%20top%20priority%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20modus%20operandi%20of%20the%20Kashmiri%20men%20reaching%20Russia%20was%20largely%20similarly%20to%20previous%20cases%20%E2%80%93%20they%20had%20been%20lured%20through%20promises%20made%20in%20a%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20%E2%80%98Baba%20Vlogs%E2%80%99%20operated%20by%20Dubai-based%20consultant%20called%20Faisal%20Khan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20information%20provided%20by%20one%20of%20the%20Kashmiri%20men%2C%20Azad%20Yusuf%20Kumar%20from%20Pulwama%E2%80%99s%20Awantipora%2C%20the%20JKSA%20said%20that%20on%20arrival%20in%20Russia%2C%20they%20were%20made%20to%20sign%20agreements%20in%20Russian%20which%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20comprehend.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESubsequently%2C%20they%20were%20transferred%20to%20the%20Russian%20army%2C%20where%20they%20underwent%20a%2015-day%20training%20program%20before%20being%20dispatched%20to%20the%20Ukraine%20border.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAzad%20has%20reportedly%20sustained%20injuries%20and%20is%20currently%20stranded%20at%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20border.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20family%20has%20provided%20documentation%20of%20the%20signed%20agreement%20in%20Russian%2C%20Azad%E2%80%99s%20current%20location%2C%20his%20photograph%2C%20and%20his%20IMO%20(International%20Maritime%20Organisation)%20number%2C%20which%20he%20has%20been%20using%20to%20contact%20them%20intermittently%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20JKSA%20spokesman%20stated.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20second%20individual%20from%20Kashmir%2C%20identified%20as%20Zahoor%20Ahmad%20Sheikh%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Kupwara%E2%80%99s%20Tangdhar%20area%2C%20is%20missing.%20Zahoor%20had%20travelled%20to%20Russia%20last%20December%2C%20reportedly%20accompanied%20by%20two%20other%20men%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fresponse-to-queries.htm%3Fdtl%2F37653%2FOfficial%2BSpokespersons%2Bresponse%2Bto%2Bmedia%2Bqueries%2Bregarding%2BIndians%2Bcaught%2Bin%2Bconflict%2Bin%2BRussia%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20Friday%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20MEA%20spokesper