d%20various%20hospitals%20and%20explored%20different%20options.%20In%202014%2C%20when%20the%20child%20was%20five%20years%20old%2C%20they%20were%20introduced%20to%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%2C%20which%20offered%20assistance.%20With%20their%20financial%20support%2C%20Sukhjot%20received%20a%20cochlear%20implant%20that%20year%20and%20is%20now%20flourishing%20in%20a%20mainstream%20school%20just%20like%20any%20other%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20daughter%20can%20now%20speak%20well%20and%20is%20a%20good%20student.%20She%20also%20paints%20very%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Rajinder%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20yearning%20to%20hear%20her%20speak.%20Now%2C%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20have%20enough%20of%20it!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1708783652.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sukhjot%20received%20a%20cochlear%20implant%20and%20is%20now%20flourishing%20in%20school%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1708783652.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1708783652-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1708783652-500x281.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1708783652-768x432.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1708783652-150x84.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343113%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESukhjot%20received%20a%20cochlear%20implant%20and%20is%20now%20flourishing%20in%20school.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341755%2Fcongenital-heart-disease-in-babies-treatment-surgery-provided-by-hans-foundation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Hans%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fa%3E%20intervention%20has%20supported%20the%20surgeries%20and%20rehabilitation%20of%20over%20900%20children%20across%2014%20hospitals%20in%20seven%20states%2C%20from%20its%20start%20in%20December%202013%20to%20date.%20Dr%20Ravi%20Bhatia%2C%20an%20ENT%20surgeon%20at%20Sarvodaya%20Hospital%20%E2%80%94%20a%20partner%20of%20THF%20%E2%80%94%20explains%20that%20a%20cochlear%20implant%20aids%20children%20with%20severe%20hearing%20loss%20in%20listening%2C%20understanding%2C%20and%20beginning%20to%20speak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20cochlear%20implant%20is%20an%20electronic%20device%20which%20is%20implanted%20through%20surgery%20into%20the%20baby%E2%80%99s%20ear.%20It%20bypasses%20the%20damaged%20hair%20cells%20of%20the%20inner%20ear%20or%20cochlea%20to%20provide%20sound%20signals%20to%20the%20brain%20by%20stimulating%20the%20inner%20ear%2C%20which%20helps%20the%20child%20to%20start%20hearing.%20There%20is%20an%20internal%20and%20external%20device%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20implant%20comprises%20an%20external%20component%20placed%20behind%20the%20ear%20and%20a%20second%20component%20surgically%20implanted%20under%20the%20skin.%20This%20surgery%20can%20be%20performed%20as%20early%20as%20six%20to%20eight%20months%20of%20age%20and%20ideally%20should%20be%20completed%20by%20the%20time%20the%20child%20reaches%20three%20years%20old%2C%20ensuring%20timely%20access%20to%20schooling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20newborn%20hearing%20screening%2C%20the%20doctors%20can%20assess%20if%20the%20baby%20has%20any%20hearing%20loss.%20Through%20a%20battery%20of%20tests%20and%20follow-ups%2C%20by%20the%20time%20the%20child%20is%20three%20to%20four%20months%20old%2C%20it%20becomes%20clear%20if%20the%20baby%20needs%20a%20cochlear%20implant%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20baby%20reaches%20eight%20months%20old%2C%20they%20are%20ready%20for%20the%20surgery%2C%20which%20typically%20lasts%20two%20and%20a%20half%20hours.%20However%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20note%20that%20the%20surgery%20alone%20addresses%20only%2020%20percent%20of%20the%20problem.%20What%E2%80%99s%20equally%20important%20is%20the%20post-surgery%20Auditory%20Verbal%20Therapy%20(AVT)%2C%20which%20spans%20two%20years%20and%20requires%20parental%20involvement%20to%20ensure%20the%20child%20develops%20spoken%20language%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETHF%20states%20that%20each%20cochlear%20implant%20procedure%20with%20the%20device%2C%20surgery%20and%20rehabilitation%20costs%20about%20Rs%208-9%20lakh%20per%20ear.%20THF%20also%20provides%20support%20for%20this%20therapy%20and%20ensures%20that%20parents%20from%20underprivileged%20backgrounds%20have%20access%20to%20therapists%20and%20can%20continue%20the%20therapy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Don%E2%80%99t%20ignore%20warning%20signs%20of%20hearing%20loss%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-16-1708783874.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cochlear%20implant%20surgery%20is%20most%20effective%20when%20done%20in%20the%200-5%20age%20group%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-16-1708783874.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-16-1708783874-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-16-1708783874-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-16-1708783874-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-16-1708783874-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343118%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECochlear%20implant%20surgery%20is%20most%20effective%20when%20done%20in%20the%200-3%20age%20group%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20like%20in%20Sukhjot%E2%80%99s%20case%2C%20many%20parents%20come%20to%20doctors%20late%2C%20says%20Dr%20Bhatia.%20This%20lack%20of%20awareness%20causes%20significant%20delays%20in%20the%20surgery%2C%20affecting%20outcomes.%20An%20internal%20study%20conducted%20by%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%20revealed%20that%20hearing%20outcomes%20among%20children%20who%20received%20implants%20between%20the%20ages%20of%20zero%20and%20three%20were%20two%20and%20a%20half%20times%20improved%20compared%20to%20those%20implanted%20at%20ages%20four%20and%20older.%20Hence%2C%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20identify%20and%20undergo%20implantation%20before%20the%20age%20of%20three%20for%20a%20favourable%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20lot%20of%20parents%20are%20in%20denial%20about%20their%20children%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F328341%2Fyunikee-empowers-deaf-persons-accessing-hearing-solutions-govt-jobs-skills%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehearing%20loss%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20India.%20Elders%20also%20support%20their%20beliefs%20saying%20that%20even%20we%20spoke%20late.%20When%20a%20child%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20listen%20to%20sounds%20or%20react%20to%20sounds%2C%20parents%20must%20raise%20a%20red%20flag.%20Go%20to%20a%20doctor%20and%20get%20your%20child%20checked%20if%20you%20notice%20anything%20wrong%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Bhatia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%20grows%20its%20commitment%20to%20supporting%20several%20life-changing%20medical%20interventions%20for%20children%20from%20underprivileged%20backgrounds%20under%20its%20larger%20umbrella%20of%20Hans%20Paediatric%20Care%2C%20support%20for%20children%20who%20need%20cochlear%20implant%20surgeries%20remains%20a%20key%20part%20of%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETHF%20works%20closely%20with%20its%20hospital%20partners%20for%20these%20surgeries.%20Doctors%20from%20the%20partner%20hospitals%20and%20their%20networks%20identify%20children%20who%20need%20support%20and%20connect%20them%20with%20the%20foundation%E2%80%99s%20programme.%20THF%20ensures%20that%20the%20family%20is%20prepared%20to%20commit%20to%20post-surgery%20therapy%20and%20maintain%20the%20device%20properly.%20Dr%20Bhatia%20emphasises%20the%20importance%20of%20periodic%20battery%20replacements%20and%20regular%20cleaning%20of%20the%20device.%20Additionally%2C%20patients%20should%20take%20precautions%20to%20avoid%20ear%20injuries%20and%20promptly%20seek%20medical%20attention%20in%20case%20of%20infections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20a%20decade%20of%20experience%20with%20the%20programme%2C%20the%20Foundation%20has%20observed%20that%20the%20success%20of%20a%20cochlear%20implant%20is%20based%20on%20a%20multitude%20of%20factors.%20The%20cause%20and%20type%20of%20hearing%20impairment%20have%20an%20effect%2C%20but%20so%20does%20the%20age%20of%20the%20child%2C%20time%20elapsed%20since%20the%20onset%20of%20hearing%20loss%2C%20active%20implant%20use%2C%20and%20also%20family%20support%20which%20affects%20the%20quality%20of%20speech%20and%20educational%20rehabilitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Bhatia%20urges%20parents%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CDo%20not%20ignore%20any%20warning%20signs%20or%20doubts.%20Just%20go%20and%20consult%20a%20doctor.%20Cochlear%20implants%20are%20nothing%20to%20be%20wary%20of%20%E2%80%93%20they%20are%20a%20well%20established%20technology%20and%20can%20change%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20life%20for%20the%20better%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C