ading%5C%22%3E5.%20Upgrade%20the%20soil%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpgrading%20your%20soil%20for%20the%20summer%20season%20is%20crucial%20to%20ensure%20that%20your%20plants%20have%20the%20nutrients%2C%20moisture%20retention%2C%20and%20drainage%20they%20need%20to%20thrive%20in%20the%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20gardening%20website%3Cem%3E%20indiagardening.com%3C%2Fem%3E%20suggests%2C%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20early%20summers%2C%20amend%20the%20garden%20soil%20to%20enhance%20the%20water%20retaining%20capability%20as%20well%20as%20aeration.%20Use%20organic%20matter%20or%20compost%20as%20it%20improves%20water%20retention%20and%20is%20also%20beneficial%20for%20microbes%20and%20worms%20in%20the%20soil.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E6.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20forget%20to%20prune%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETimely%20pruning%20your%20garden%20can%20go%20a%20long%20way.%20Remove%20dead%20or%20diseased%20foliage%2C%20and%20prune%20back%20overgrown%20branches%20to%20improve%20air%20circulation%20and%20prevent%20fungal%20diseases.%20Deadhead%20spent%20flowers%20to%20encourage%20continuous%20blooming%20and%20remove%20any%20weeds%20that%20may%20compete%20with%20your%20plants%20for%20water%20and%20nutrients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E7.%20Water%2C%20then%20water%20some%20more!%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20scorching%20heat%20of%20the%20sun%2C%20ensuring%20your%20plants%20receive%20the%20appropriate%20amount%20of%20water%20is%20crucial.%20Opt%20for%20deep%20watering%20less%20often%20to%20promote%20deep%20root%20growth%20and%20enhance%20drought%20tolerance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20an%20%3Cem%3EHT%3C%2Fem%3E%20article%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20best%20way%20to%20gauge%20that%20is%20to%20water%20your%20plants%20in%20the%20morning.%20If%20the%20soil%20is%20dry%20again%20by%20evening%2C%20you%20know%20your%20plants%20need%20to%20be%20watered%20twice%20a%20day.%E2%80%9D%20The%20health%20of%20your%20plants%20also%20depends%20on%20what%20